%5B%7B%22title%22%3A%22It%20feels%20like%20whenever%20I'm%20not%20cooking%20for%20my%20family%2C%20I'm%20thinking%20about%20groceries%20or%20meal%20planning.%20It's%20overwhelming.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221320%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20with%20her%20son%20at%20the%20table.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b58a394eb4c909fb2d961%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22974%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20meal%20plans%2C%20cooks%2C%20and%20grocery%20shops%20for%20her%20family.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Tonilyn%20Hornung%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EI%20often%20feel%20like%20I'm%20carrying%20the%20entire%20'food%20load'%20for%20my%20family.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI'm%20the%20one%20who%20grocery%20shops%2C%20meal%20plans%2C%20and%20cooks%20for%20all%20of%20us.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EIt%20can%20be%20lonely%20and%20overwhelming%2C%20so%20I%20started%20asking%20my%20husband%20for%20help.%20%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BDid%20you%20see%20the%20lights%3F%26quot%3B%20my%20husband%20asked%20enthusiastically.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20fact%2C%20I%20had%20seen%20the%20outdoor%20lights%20he%20hung%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-quick-trip-relax-before-busy-summer-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epreparation%20for%20the%20summer%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20told%20him%20they%20looked%20great%2C%20to%20which%20he%20replied%20proudly%2C%20%26quot%3BSee%2C%20I%20do%20things%20around%20here.%26quot%3B%20Huh%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20watched%20him%20walk%20off%20into%20the%20well-lit%20patio%20and%20stayed%20back%2C%20slightly%20confused.%20Did%20he%20mean%20he%20accomplished%20%3Cem%3Emany%3C%2Fem%3E%20things%20around%20here%2C%20or%20just%20this%20%3Cem%3Eone%20%3C%2Fem%3Ething%3F%20The%20thought%20came%20in%20fast%3A%20Was%20he%20comparing%20this%20to%20everyday%20tasks%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20ones%20I%20did%2C%20you%20know%E2%80%A6%20everyday%3F%20And%20what%20about%20all%20the%20meals%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a362dbd8-d1d8-46e2-9fdd-22b07b3159ea%5C%22%3EI%20am%20constantly%20carrying%20the%20'food%20load'%20for%20my%20family%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20plenty%20of%20evidence%20that%20suggests%20my%20family%20thinks%20I'm%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftiny-ai-startup-hired-private-chef-costs-productivity-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epersonal%20chef%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I'm%20the%20one%20doing%20the%20shopping%2C%20menu%20planning%2C%20prepping%2C%20cooking%2C%20and%20scheduling%20meal%20times.%20While%20I%20do%20enjoy%20many%20aspects%20of%20organizing%20(clutter-free%20kitchen%20countertops%20are%20the%20best)%2C%20others%20feel%20more%20like%20chores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%2C%20there%20are%20the%20constant%20questions%20I%20have%20to%20ask%20myself%3A%20What's%20for%20dinner%20tomorrow%3F%20Do%20we%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsave-up-to-80-percent-on-groceries-breaking-one-rule-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20groceries%3C%2Fa%3E%3F%20What%20needs%20to%20be%20eaten%20before%20it%20goes%20bad%3F%20What's%20everyone's%20schedule%20tomorrow%3F%20All%20those%20run%20through%20my%20head%20like%20our%20toddler%20used%20to%20run%20through%20our%20living%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELooking%20back%2C%20I%20can%20trace%20the%20evolution.%20When%20our%20son%20was%20little%2C%20I%20was%20the%20boss%20of%20his%20schedule.%20My%20little%20one%20and%20I%20ate%20at%20different%20times%20from%20my%20husband%2C%20and%20this%20worked%20for%20us.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20time%20went%20on%2C%20our%20kiddo%20started%20eating%20at%20regular%20mealtimes%2C%20but%20I%20stayed%20on%20as%20the%20default%20meal%20planner.%20No%20way%20could%20I%20have%20predicted%20I'd%20be%20left%20alone%20in%20this%20space%2C%20because%20other%20tasks%20in%20our%20house%20had%20been%20fluid%20and%20flexible.%20My%20husband%20and%20I%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-startups-robotics-pay-film-chores-encord-micro1-scale-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efold%20laundry%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20empty%20the%20dishwasher%2C%20vacuum%2C%20and%20more.%20As%20the%20roles%20in%20our%20new%20family%20became%20more%20defined%2C%20Master%20Chef%20Meal%20Planner%20solidified%20as%20my%20chore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224db0241e-c50b-4d86-98a6-f18db9d6a5a5%5C%22%3EIt's%20just%20one%20part%20of%20what%20I%20do%20for%20my%20family%2C%20but%20it%20makes%20me%20feel%20overwhelmed%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fonlinelibrary.wiley.com%2Fdoi%2F10.1111%2Fjomf.12762%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EStudies%20show%3C%2Fa%3E%20a%20persistent%20gender%20divide%20in%20household%20chores%2C%20with%20women%20often%20handling%2073%25%20of%20cognitive%20chores%20and%20spending%20roughly%20twice%20as%20much%20time%20on%20housework%20as%20men.%20Well%2C%20that's%20a%20lot%2C%20and%20clearly%20reflected%20in%20my%20family.%20The%20fact%20that%20the%20mental%20load%20of%20mothers%20is%20more%20often%20discussed%20recently%2C%20both%20in%20popular%20culture%20and%20among%20mom%20groups%20and%20my%20friends%2C%20is%20helpful%20because%20it%20validates%20my%20experience%20and%20names%20the%20feelings%20surrounding%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECarrying%20the%20'food%20load'%20for%20my%20family%20is%20just%20one%20part%20of%20what%20I%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20other%20mothers%20%E2%80%94%20do%2C%20but%20it's%20one%20that%20leaves%20me%20feeling%20overwhelmed%2C%20tired%2C%20and%20lonely%2C%20even%20just%20thinking%20about%20it.%20This%20labor%20is%20specific%20and%20nuanced.%20While%20a%20lot%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fraising-kids-teens-share-household-responsibilities-equally-chores-mental-load-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehousehold%20tasks%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20repetitive%2C%20many%20are%20performed%20only%20weekly%20or%20monthly%E2%80%94%20and%20yes%2C%20in%20some%20cases%2C%20only%20done%20once%20in%20a%20while%2C%20like%20hanging%20patio%20lights.%20Meals%20and%20snacks%20are%20often%20either%20demanded%20or%20in%20preparation%20all%20day%2C%20every%20day.%20My%20brain%20is%20full%20of%20menus%20and%20food%20options%20for%20breakfast%2C%20lunch%2C%20dinner%2C%20and%20everything%20in%20between.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ff79dfc6-c53f-46a3-a1c0-863d7468849a%5C%22%3EI%20asked%20my%20husband%20for%20help%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20these%20small%20daily%20decisions%20add%20up%20and%20feel%20relentless%2C%20and%20that's%20when%20the%20decision-making%20fatigue%20sets%20in.%20For%20me%2C%20it%20shows%20up%20as%20impatience%20and%20resentment%20%E2%80%94%20that%20I'm%20not%20always%20great%20at%20keeping%20to%20myself.%20I%20feel%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparenting-resentment-marriage-gratitude-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edisconnected%20from%20my%20husband%3C%2Fa%3E.%20And%20since%20I%20don't%20enjoy%20feeling%20separated%20from%20the%20people%20I%20love%20most%2C%20I%20reach%20out%20for%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHey%2C%20honey%2C%20can%20you%20help%20me%20plan%20meals%20this%20week%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20asked%20my%20partner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOf%20course%2C%20what%20do%20you%20want%20me%20to%20buy%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYeah%2C%20not%20exactly%20the%20mental-space%20freeing%20help%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%20Making%20a%20grocery%20list%20for%20him%20means%20I'm%20still%20the%20one%20making%20the%20menu%20and%20giving%20instructions%2C%20so%20while%20well-intentioned%2C%20this%20is%20more%20of%20an%20extra%20step%20on%20top%20of%20all%20the%20others%2C%20not%20a%20relief.%20I've%20tried%20talking%20about%20how%20this%20task%20weighs%20me%20down%2C%20but%20somehow%20we%20still%20slip%20back%20into%20our%20well-defined%20roles.%20What's%20going%20to%20help%20me%20feel%20supported%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20to%20give%20up%2C%20I%20tried%20a%20different%2C%20more%20direct%20approach%3A%20%26quot%3BHey%2C%20honey%2C%20Friday%20night%20is%20taco%20night%2C%20so%20can%20you%20cook%20on%20Fridays%3F%26quot%3B%20And%20that's%20how%20Taco%20Night%20began.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20has%20taken%20over%20Friday%2C%20Tuesday%2C%20and%20Saturday%20dinners%20with%20a%20consistent%20menu%20for%20each%20night.%20His%20brain%20likes%20structure%2C%20and%20this%20way%20he%20knows%20what%20he%20needs%20and%20which%20days%20he's%20our%20head%20chef%20%E2%80%94%20taking%20some%20meal%20planning%20off%20the%20table%20for%20me.%20We're%20working%20toward%20a%20more%20balanced%20schedule%20for%20all%20of%20us%20%E2%80%94%20my%20son%20included.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20helped%20my%20husband%20see%20what%20I%20do%20on%20the%20days%20he's%20not%20the%20one%20cooking.%20Making%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finvisble-labor-home-mom-teaches-kids-notice-and-do-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einvisible%20labor%3C%2Fa%3E%20visible%20helps%20reduce%20stress%20and%20foster%20teamwork%20in%20our%20family%2C%20because%20the%20food%20load%20definitely%20isn't%20a%20load%20to%20be%20carried%20alone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-invisible-labor-groceries-food-cooking-family-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779189721000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b58acecd7cc1332bb0ce5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmom-invisible-labor-groceries-food-cooking-family-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22I'm%20always%20cooking%2C%20meal%20planning%2C%20or%20grocery%20shopping%20for%20my%20family%2C%20and%20it's%20overwhelming.%20I%20finally%20asked%20my%20husband%20for%20help.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Tonilyn%20Hornung)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Jensen%20Huang%20says%20he%20wouldn't%20start%20Nvidia%20again%20if%20he%20knew%20the%20pain%20ahead%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20waves%20during%20his%20China%20trip.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a06f84cabc4e9d88574a565%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222335%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EBuilding%20Nvidia%20required%20enduring%20humiliation%2C%20sacrifice%2C%20and%20near-failure%2C%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20said.%3Cp%3EBrendan%20SMIALOWSKI%20%2F%20AFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EJensen%20Huang%20said%20Nvidia's%20rise%20came%20with%20years%20of%20humiliation%20and%20near-collapse.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ENvidia's%20CEO%20said%20he%20wouldn't%20found%20the%20company%20again%2C%20knowing%20the%20pain%20involved.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHuang%20said%20surviving%20Nvidia's%20darkest%20years%20required%20%26quot%3Bforgetting%20yesterday.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EStarting%20Nvidia%20all%20over%20again%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-graduation-speech-ai-jobs-anxiety-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EJensen%20Huang%3C%2Fa%3E%20says%20no%20chance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20interview%20on%20the%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Built%20This%26quot%3B%20podcast%20with%20Guy%20Raz%20released%20on%20Monday%2C%20Huang%20reflected%20on%20the%20years%20of%20pressure%2C%20humiliation%2C%20near-bankruptcy%20scares%2C%20and%20personal%20sacrifice%20that%20came%20with%20turning%20Nvidia%20into%20the%20world's%20most%20valuable%20semiconductor%20company%20with%20a%20market%20cap%20of%20%245.3%20trillion%2C%20and%20the%20dominant%20force%20behind%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-memory-chip-boom-next-trillion-dollar-company-sk-hynix-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20boom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Nvidia%20was%20founded%20in%201993%20and%20went%20public%20in%201999.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSuppose%20I%20knew%20everything%20then%20that%20I%20now%20know%20%E2%80%94%20how%20hard%20it%20is%20and%20all%20of%20the%20pain%20and%20suffering%20and%20all%20the%20embarrassment%20and%20humiliation%20and%20all%20the%20setbacks%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%2C%20asking%20himself%20if%20he%20would%20start%20again%3F%20%26quot%3BThe%20answer%2C%20absolutely%20not.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228d8e67e8-dbe5-421c-8368-0f761b51e3d6%5C%22%3EThe%20cost%20of%20success%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20billionaire%20CEO%20said%20many%20founders%20understate%20the%20emotional%20toll%20of%20building%20a%20company%20because%20people%20only%20focus%20on%20the%20final%20outcome.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20your%20question%20is%20knowing%20how%20Nvidia%20turned%20out%2C%20knowing%20the%20contribution%20we've%20made%20to%20the%20world%2C%20knowing%20the%20consequence%20of%20the%20company%20today%2C%20how%20it%20impacts%20so%20many%20different%20industries%2C%20all%20of%20the%20benefits%20that%20we%20have%20accrued%20as%20a%20result%20of%20our%20success%2C%20do%20I%20love%20those%20things%3F%20The%20answer%20is%20yes%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BBut%20that%20wasn't%20the%20question.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20described%20periods%20in%20the%20mid-2010s%20when%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-stock-price-record-high-ai-trade-jensen-huang-markets-investing-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20stock%20price%3C%2Fa%3E%20collapsed%20while%20the%20company%20continued%20pouring%20money%20into%20CUDA%2C%20the%20software%20platform%20that%20later%20became%20foundational%20to%20modern%20AI%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%202008%20financial%20crisis%2C%20Nvidia%20shares%20dropped%20by%20about%2085%25%20from%20their%20late-2007%20highs.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20many%20investors%20doubted%20the%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20was%20embarrassing.%20It%20was%20humiliating%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou're%20the%20only%20face%20that%20everybody%20hates.%20Your%20employees%20are%20probably%20embarrassed%20for%20you.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20also%20survived%20multiple%20existential%20crises%20during%20its%20early%20years%2C%20including%20failed%20chips%2C%20layoffs%2C%20and%20moments%20when%20Huang%20believed%20the%20company%20was%20only%20weeks%20away%20from%20running%20out%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%201996%2C%20Nvidia%20almost%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-quiz-jensen-huang-ai-gpu-blackwell-4-trillion-nvda-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewent%20out%20of%20business%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20failing%20to%20deliver%20a%20graphics%20chip%20for%20Sega.%20Sega%20provided%20Nvidia%20with%20a%20%245%20million%20investment%20that%20kept%20the%20company%20afloat.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou'll%20be%20going%20out%20of%20business.%20You'll%20have%20to%20lay%20people%20off%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%2C%20describing%20the%20reality%20of%20startup%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ca6e97a2-c566-4eaa-a6bd-bd5f15eaa0bf%5C%22%3EForgetting%20the%20pain%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20the%20only%20way%20he%20endured%20was%20by%20training%20himself%20not%20to%20dwell%20on%20setbacks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20spent%20all%20my%20time%20forgetting%20yesterday%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20do%20they%20teach%20athletes%3F%20Forget%20the%20last%20point.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20CEO%20also%20reflected%20on%20the%20personal%20cost%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftech-memo-nvidia-millionaires-small-workforce-stock-awards-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20rise%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Huang%20said%20he%20missed%20many%20of%20his%20children's%20karate%20tournaments%20while%20balancing%20nonstop%20work%20and%20graduate%20school%20at%20Stanford.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20missed%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20praising%20his%20wife%20for%20%26quot%3Btaking%20care%20of%20everything.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20Huang%20said%20Nvidia's%20success%20came%20from%20staying%20committed%20to%20ideas%20others%20dismissed%2C%20especially%20the%20belief%20that%20graphics%20chips%20could%20someday%20power%20a%20new%20era%20of%20computing%20beyond%20video%20games.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20forget%20that%20the%20pain%20and%20suffering%20necessary%2C%20the%20endurance%20necessary%20to%20do%20something%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20because%20you're%20always%20looking%20forward%20and%20forgetting%20the%20past.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-wouldnt-start-nvidia-again-knowing-pain-setbacks-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779189253000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0c33ceecd7cc1332bb0fbd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjensen-huang-wouldnt-start-nvidia-again-knowing-pain-setbacks-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Nvidia%20CEO%20said%20running%20the%20semiconductor%20company%20required%20years%20of%20pressure%2C%20humiliation%2C%20near-bankruptcy%20scares%2C%20and%20personal%20sacrifice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bharat%20Forge%20signed%20MoU%20to%20build%20marine%20gas%20turbine%20facility%20in%20Andhra%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779189238000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2024-08%2F09%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F17