%20that%20reward%20busyness.%20It%20advocates%20for%20'talent%20density'%20and%20autonomy%2C%20urging%20managers%20to%20assess%20tasks%20by%20their%20impact%20rather%20than%20time%20spent.%20This%20approach%2C%20though%20sometimes%20uncomfortable%2C%20remains%20relevant%20for%20boosting%20genuine%20productivity%20by%20focusing%20on%20tangible%20achievements.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-reed-hastings-netflix-culture-memo-says-working-harder-can-quietly-hurt-your-company%2Farticleshow%2F131166750.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-reed-hastings-netflix-culture-memo-says-working-harder-can-quietly-hurt-your-company%2Famp_articleshow%2F131166750.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwhy-reed-hastings-netflix-culture-memo-says-working-harder-can-quietly-hurt-your-company%2Famp_articleshow%2F131166750.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Bad%20news%2C%2030-somethings%3A%20You'll%20likely%20never%20be%20truly%20AI%20native%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Employees%20at%20the%20Manycore%20Tech%20Inc.%20offices%20in%20Hangzhou%2C%20China%2C%20in%20April%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0af52cabc4e9d88574af1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EFormer%20OpenAI%20robotics%20lead%20Caitlin%20Kalinowski%20says%20the%20most%20AI-native%20workers%20are%20in%20their%20early%2020s.%3Cp%3EQilai%20Shen%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EA%20former%20OpenAI%20robotics%20lead%20says%20engineers%20in%20their%2030s%20aren't%20truly%20AI%20native.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECaitlin%20Kalinowski%20said%20young%20engineers%20use%20AI%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20and%20solve%20faster%20than%20older%20peers.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ETech%20leaders%20from%20Reddit%20to%20LinkedIn%20say%20AI-native%20graduates%20have%20a%20growing%20edge%20at%20work.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%2030-plus%2C%20you're%20likely%20already%20at%20a%20disadvantage%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20according%20to%20former%20OpenAI%20robotics%20lead%20Caitlin%20Kalinowski%2C%20who%20said%20that%20the%20only%20truly%20AI%20native%20people%20right%20now%20are%20those%20in%20their%20early%2020s%20who%20grew%20up%20solving%20problems%20with%20AI%20from%20the%20ground%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20%26quot%3Buse%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20so%20natively%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20it's%20like%20baked%20into%20their%20engineering%20process%2C%26quot%3B%20Kalinowski%20said%20on%20an%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BLenny's%26quot%3B%20podcast%20released%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski%20worked%20at%20Apple%2C%20Oculus%20VR%2C%20and%20Meta%20before%20joining%20OpenAI's%20robotics%20division%20as%20a%20Member%20of%20Technical%20Staff%20between%202024%20and%202026.%20She%20now%20advises%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fyoung-founders-raising-millions-for-their-ai-startups-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20startups%20on%20product%20strategy%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20said%20in%20her%20experience%2C%20the%20most%20striking%20shift%20she's%20seeing%20is%20how%20younger%20engineers%20interact%20with%20the%20technology%20itself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20very%20hard%20to%20find%20someone%20who's%20in%20their%2030s%20who%20can%20be%20truly%20fully%20AI%20native%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22f250df7f-cb42-49cc-b461-9a6fd74e1995%5C%22%3E'We%20need%20these%20folks'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski%20said%20AI%20is%20embedded%20into%20how%20younger%20engineers%20think%20and%20solve%20problems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20approaching%20their%20problem-solving%20completely%20differently%20because%20they're%20using%20AI%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20for%20everything%2C%20and%20they're%20much%20faster%2C%20actually%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20need%20these%20folks%20to%20teach%20us%20how%20to%20think%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOther%20tech%20leaders%2C%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freddit-ceo-steve-huffman-new-grads-great-hires-ai-native-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EReddit%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Steve%20Huffman%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fotis-elevator-ceo-says-grads-have-advantage-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EOtis%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Judy%20Marks%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-native-grads-will-outperform-junior-engineers-says-box-ceo-levie-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBox%20CEO%3C%2Fa%3E%20Aaron%20Levie%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freid-hoffman-gen-z-enormously-attractive-employers-for-one-reason-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ELinkedIn%20cofounder%3C%2Fa%3E%20Reid%20Hoffman%2C%20have%20also%20said%20that%20AI-native%20younger%20workers%20may%20have%20a%20major%20advantage%20in%20the%20workplace%20because%20they%20grew%20up%20using%20AI%20tools%20instinctively%20rather%20than%20having%20to%20adapt%20to%20them%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20shift%20is%20already%20influencing%20how%20companies%20operate.%20Meta%2C%20for%20example%2C%20has%20been%20pushing%20employees%20to%20become%20more%20%26quot%3BAI-native%26quot%3B%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmetas-reality-labs-shifts-to-ai-native-pods-efficiency-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eembedding%20AI%20tools%3C%2Fa%3E%20into%20coding%20and%20day-to-day%20workflows.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski's%20comments%20also%20come%20amid%20growing%20anxiety%20that%20AI%20could%20hollow%20out%20entry-level%20tech%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20Kalinowski%20sees%20a%20more%20nuanced%20future%3A%20smaller%20teams%2C%20not%20necessarily%20junior-less%20ones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20see%20it%20that%20way%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%2C%20referring%20to%20fears%20that%20junior%20roles%20in%20tech%20firms%20could%20be%20made%20obsolete%20because%20of%20AI.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20need%20them.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKalinowski%20compared%20today's%20AI-native%20generation%20to%20early%20internet%20natives%20who%20grew%20up%20alongside%20the%20web%20and%20smartphones%2C%20giving%20them%20an%20intuitive%20advantage%20older%20workers%20lacked.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20to%20accept%20that%20we're%20not%20native%20in%20these%20new%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20of%20older%20engineers%20and%20tech%20workers%20adapting%20to%20AI%20later%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-native-college-graduates-gen-z-have-an-edge-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779187170000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0af52cabc4e9d88574af1b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fai-native-college-graduates-gen-z-have-an-edge-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20OpenAI%20robotics%20leader%20Caitlin%20Kalinowski%20says%20truly%20AI-native%20workers%20are%20mostly%2020%20and%2021%20years%20old.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22tspirlet%40insider.com%20(Thibault%20Spirlet)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20Maharashtra%20Files%20is%20all%20set%20to%20hit%20theatres%20on%20THIS%20date%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%