rub%20Ai%20is%20solid%20vacuum%2C%20but%20a%20better%20mop.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDyson's%20first%20robot%20vacuum%2C%20the%20360%20Vis%20Nav%2C%20was%20powerful%20but%20hard%20to%20recommend%20for%20many%20homes.%20It%20had%20strong%20suction%20and%20a%20distinctive%20design%2C%20but%20the%20navigation%20lagged%20behind%20the%20best%20robot%20vacuums%2C%20and%20it%20didn't%20mop.%20The%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D8eda40f7811a3bee97806db9eb9d2b919dd425752eb8fbebfd5f9b4f42603837%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dyson.com%252Fvacuum-cleaners%252Frobot%252Fspot-scrub-ai%252Fblack%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDyson%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20much%20more%20competitive%20follow-up%20among%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-robot-vacuum-mop%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebest%20robot%20vacuum%20and%20mops%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%2C%20Dyson%20added%20mopping%2C%20a%20proper%20self-emptying%20and%20self-cleaning%20dock%2C%20LiDAR-assisted%20mapping%2C%20and%20improved%20object%20avoidance%20and%20stain-detection%20features%20designed%20to%20send%20the%20robot%20back%20over%20messes%20that%20need%20extra%20attention.%20After%20testing%20dozens%20of%20robot%20vacuums%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20and%20using%20the%20360%20Vis%20Nav%20regularly%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20I%20can%20say%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20is%20a%20major%20step%20forward.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20name%20suggests%2C%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20is%20especially%20focused%20on%20mopping.%20It's%20excellent%20at%20it%2C%20too.%20If%20your%20home%20is%20mostly%20carpet%2C%20you%20won't%20get%20as%20much%20value%20from%20this%20robot.%20%3Cstrong%3EIt's%20a%20solid%20vacuum%2C%20but%20a%20better%20mop.%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20a%20few%20flaws%20too%3A%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20can%20be%20messy%20around%20its%20docking%20station%20and%20is%20too%20bulky%20to%20get%20under%20cabinet%20toe%20kicks.%20Though%20these%20could%20be%20nitpicks%2C%20in%20general%2C%20Dyson%20has%20a%20robot%20you%20should%20be%20considering%20if%20you%20want%20constant%2C%20hands-free%20cleaning%20maintenance.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDyson%20deal%20alert%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAt%20%241%2C200%2C%20this%20vacuum%20falls%20into%20premium%20territory%2C%20and%20expectations%20are%20even%20higher%20about%20how%20it%20performs.%20We%20spotted%20it%20on%20sale%20for%20%24350%20off%2C%20for%20the%20first%20time%2C%20making%20it%20an%20even%20more%20attractive%20package.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Caside%3E%5Cn%3Ch4%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221f55bd51-4298-4a95-98a8-56735dccf276%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22How%20I%20tested%5C%22%3EHow%20I%20tested%3C%2Fh4%3E%3Cp%3EI%20tested%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20over%20several%20weeks%20in%20my%20home%2C%20running%20it%20through%20everyday%20cleaning%20jobs%20and%20controlled%20mess%20tests%20with%20rice%2C%20crushed%20cereal%2C%20flour%2C%20jelly%2C%20soda%2C%20maple%20syrup%2C%20faux%20pet%20waste%2C%20and%20cables.%20I%20also%20compared%20it%20to%20my%20experience%20with%20the%20Dyson%20360%20Vis%20Nav%2C%20which%20I%20used%20regularly%20for%20more%20than%20a%20year%2C%20and%20to%20my%20testing%20of%20dozens%20of%20robot%20vacuums%20over%20the%20last%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Faside%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22625ee239-5448-4542-aead-bd5ab4b72066%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Design%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EDyson%20traded%20personality%20for%20practicality%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22side%20by%20side%20of%20the%20underside%20and%20base%20station%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a076bbeabc4e9d88574a95b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20look%20at%20the%20underside%20of%20the%20Dyson%20and%20the%20docking%20station%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20understand%20the%20significance%20of%20the%20Dyson%20Spot%20%26amp%3B%20Scrub%20Ai%2C%20it's%20worth%20touching%20on%20the%20previous%20attempt%3A%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dd6ab8427ebf561949858b5543e4b0e7893725393e7d3f1f7d4bf64ca8bd26886%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FDyson-360-Vis-Robot-Vacuum%252Fdp%252FB0CT95LTCJ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDyson%20360%20Vis%20Nav%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20one%20has%20strong%20suction%2C%20a%20big%20dustbin%2C%20and%20beefy%20wheels%20to%20traverse%20high-pile%20rugs.%20Unfortunately%2C%20its%20navigation%20made%20it%20hard%20to%20recommend%20for%20complex%20floor%20plans.%20And%2C%20it%20only%20vacuums.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20AI%2C%20Dyson%20addressed%20these%20issues%3A%20It%20adds%20lidar%20to%20its%20camera-based%20vision%20system%2C%20gains%20mopping%2C%20and%20comes%20with%20a%20full%20docking%20station.%20It%20also%20integrates%20the%20green%20laser%20illumination%2C%20found%20on%20some%20of%20its%20cordless%20vacuum%20products%2C%20that%20highlights%20what%20the%20eye%20can't%20see.%20It's%20more%20useful%20when%20you're%20the%20one%20doing%20the%20navigating%20than%20the%20robot%3B%20here%20it's%20almost%20distracting.%20Overall%20though%2C%20it's%20a%20tremendous%20leap%20forward%20from%20the%20original%20if%20you%20want%20a%20more%20autonomous%20cleaner.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20first%20saw%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20in%20Berlin%20during%20the%20company's%202025%20unveiling%2C%20the%20most%20surprising%20thing%20about%20it%20was%20how%20much%20it%20resembled%20other%20robot%20vacuums%20on%20the%20market.%20It%20ditched%20its%20classic%20Dyson%20flair%20for%20a%20mostly%20plain%2C%20black%20design.%20The%20most%20noticeable%20%26quot%3BDyson%26quot%3B%20attribute%20that%20remains%20is%20the%20clear%20dustbin%20on%20the%20docking%20station.%20I%20wish%20it%20had%20more%20of%20the%20company's%20flair%2C%20but%20the%20more%20important%20point%20is%20that%20it's%20improved%20over%20the%20last%20version.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22e78d76d7-6cb0-490b-b7b4-0898f6b88ed7%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22App%20and%20set%20up%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EMapping%20was%20quick%2C%20even%20if%20the%20app%20feels%20busy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222400%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dyson%20app%20screenshots%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a076a9cecd7cc1332bb03ee%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20MyDyson%20app%20is%20the%20hub%20for%20all%20things%20Dyson%20products.%20For%20the%20robot%2C%20the%20app%20will%20show%20where%20obstacles%20(orange%20dot)%20and%20extra%20stains%20(green%20icon)%20were%20detected%20as%20well%20as%20its%20cleaning%20path%2C%20and%20how%20long%20it'll%20take%20to%20clean.%20It%20also%20differentiates%20between%20floor%20type.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20MyDyson%20app%20has%20all%20the%20modern%20features%20of%20other%20competitors%2C%20including%20real-time%20tracking%2C%20room%20selection%2C%20targeted%20spot%20cleaning%2C%20and%20adjustable%20vacuum%20and%20mop%20settings.%20It's%20perfectly%20fine%20for%20controlling%20the%20unit.%20It's%20easy%20enough%20to%20use%2C%20but%20because%20the%20app%20also%20houses%20controls%20for%20other%20Dyson%20products%20like%20air%20purifiers%2C%20hair%20tools%20and%20headphones%2C%20it%20can%20feel%20crowded.%20Whether%20having%20everything%20in%20one%20space%20is%20more%20convenient%20or%20distracting%20will%20likely%20depend%20on%20how%20many%20Dyson%20products%20you%20use%20regularly.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20initial%20mapping%20was%20fast%20and%20mostly%20accurate%2C%20but%20the%20interior%20walls%20were%20less%20structured%20and%20more%20wavy-looking%20than%20they%20are%20in%20apps%20from%20Roborock%20or%20Eufy.%20This%20didn't%20impact%20cleaning%2C%20but%20could%20make%20precise%20spot%20cleaning%20area%20harder%20to%20gauge.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c8d35502-2748-4876-a41c-67622d07b49b%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Vacuuming%20performance%5C%22%3EIt's%20a%20good%20vacuum%2C%20but%20not%20the%20reason%20to%20buy%20it%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI%20primarily%20used%20the%20Auto%20setting%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20how%20it%20would%20do%20on%20its%20own.%20When%20the%20Auto%20mode%20didn't%20perform%20quite%20well%20enough%20in%20my%20tests%2C%20I%20reran%20tougher%20messes%20on%20Boost%20to%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20its%20top%20performance%2C%20which%20is%20probably%20only%20needed%20for%20the%20bigger%20messes.%20Auto%20worked%20fine%20on%20a%20day-to-day%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22aded8d02-037c-4ea1-9cbd-b08bf61802c9%5C%22%3EIt%20handled%20everyday%20crumbs%20better%20than%20fine%20dust%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dyson%20robot%20on%20hardwood%20floor%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0766e9abc4e9d88574a922%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20suggest%20activating%20boost%20mode%20to%20make%20sure%20it%20gets%20larger%20groups%20of%20debris%20on%20the%20first%20go.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20has%20a%20top%20suction%20level%20of%2018%2C000Pa.%20This%20pales%20in%20the%20spec%20comparison%20to%20other%20new%20units%2C%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Froborock-saros-20-review%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERoborock%20Saros%2020%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20has%20a%20top%20suction%20level%20of%2033%2C000Pa.%20In%20practice%2C%20the%20number%20difference%20was%20less%20significant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20normal%20debris%20vacuuming%2C%20the%20kind%20of%20crumbs%20that%20gather%20on%20the%20kitchen%20floor%20throughout%20the%20day%20in%20a%20house%20with%20kids%2C%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20did%20well%20at%20sucking%20those%20things%20up.%20I%20sprinkled%20around%2020%20grams%20of%20food%20items%20like%20rice%2C%20crushed%20up%20cereal%2C%20and%20flour%20on%20the%20floor%20and%20ran%20separate%2C%20targeted%20tests%20for%20each.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20did%20the%20best%20at%20vacuuming%20the%20Cheerios%2C%20which%20I%20walked%20over%20and%20crushed%20up%20most%20of%20first.%20It%20picked%20up%20around%2093%25%20of%20them.%20The%20unit%20performed%20well%20with%20the%20other%20items%2C%20too%2C%20but%2C%20like%20most%20robots%2C%20it%20tended%20to%20scatter%20some%20rice%20grains%20outside%20the%20test%20area.%20The%20flour%20left%20a%20visible%20trail%20of%20white%20powder%20from%20its%20wheels%20as%20it%20rolled%20back%20to%20its%20docking%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%204.3%20inches%20thick%2C%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20is%20also%20taller%2C%20and%20can't%20fit%20under%20cabinet%20toe%20kicks%2C%20while%20some%20other%20premium%20robots%20like%20Roborock%20Saros%20collection%2C%20which%20are%203.14%20inches%2C%20can%20fit%20under%20without%20issue.%20That's%20not%20a%20dealbreaker%20on%20the%20whole%2C%20but%20the%20robot's%20slight%20bulk%20is%20something%20to%20keep%20in%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2264090c1f-71a9-4057-b89b-5e04a0ab75b3%5C%22%3EC%3Cstrong%3Eapable%20on%20carpet%2C%20but%20better%20on%20bare%20floors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dyson%20robot%20on%20a%20carpet%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0766e9ecd7cc1332bb03b9%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dyson%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20ramps%20up%20the%20suction%20when%20it%20detects%20carpet.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20can%20auto-detect%20hard%20surfaces%20and%20carpet%20and%20identify%20the%20different%20floor%20materials%20in%20the%20mobile%20app.%20I%20sprinkled%20a%20heavy%20dose%20of%20flour%2C%20around%2020%20grams%2C%20on%20a%20low-pile%20rug%20and%20set%20it%20to%20a%20targeted%20run.%20It%20sucked%20up%20about%2075%25%20of%20the%20mess%20on%20Auto%20mode%2C%20then%20again%20on%20Boost%20mode%2C%20which%20got%20the%20total%20amount%20picked%20up%20closer%20to%2085%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERemoving%20fine%20powder%20from%20carpet%20is%20the%20hardest%20of%20all%20the%20tests.%20The%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20performs%20about%20the%20same%20as%20other%20robots%20like%20the%20recent%20Roborock%20Saros%2020%20here.%20It%20fared%20much%20better%20on%20carpet%2C%20picking%20up%20rice%20and%20crushed%20up%20Cheerios%20in%20two%20separate%20tests.%20It%20got%20nearly%20every%20grain%20of%20white%20rice%20in%20that%20test%20and%20only%20missed%20a%20few%20crumbs%20with%20the%20cereal%20one.%20The%20type%20of%20carpet%20and%20its%20pile%20height%20will%20play%20a%20big%20role%20in%20how%20well%20it%20does%20in%20this%20area%2C%20but%20for%20my%20short%20rugs%2C%20it%20performed%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%220d38623e-9335-4227-903e-1934427349b6%5C%22%3EHair%20tangles%20were%20barely%20an%20issue%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20ran%20for%20a%20few%20weeks%20in%20a%20house%20with%20two%20women%20and%20a%20non-shedding%20dog.%20While%20there%20might%20not%20be%20as%20much%20hair%20as%20in%20some%20other%20homes%2C%20I%20can%20assure%20you%20there%20is%20at%20least%20some%20that%20gets%20left%20on%20the%20floors.%20The%20good%20news%20is%20that%20there%20was%20never%20more%20than%20a%20single%20strand%20visible%20on%20the%20roller%20brush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22a2a27570-534d-4f02-ac18-dca61c44ef15%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Mopping%20performance%5C%22%3EThe%20mop%20is%20the%20star%20of%20the%20show%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dyson%20robot%20mopping%20on%20hardwood%20floor%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0766e994eb4c909fb2d070%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20roller%20style%20mop%20constantly%20flushes%20the%20brushroll%20with%20fresh%20water%2C%20which%20prevents%20smears%20and%20spreading%20more%20dirt%20across%20the%20floors.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20there's%20a%20standout%20area%20of%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%2C%20it's%20the%20mopping.%20This%20is%20the%20main%20reason%20to%20consider%20buying%20this%20unit%20over%20another%20one.%20I%20mean%2C%20it%20should%20be%20good%20because%20it's%20right%20there%20in%20the%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20primary%20reason%20this%20unit%20excels%20is%20its%20single%20mopping%20roller%20brush.%20During%20cleaning%2C%20fresh%20water%20is%20constantly%20flushed%20through%20as%20the%20brush%20spins%2C%20so%20that%20it's%20less%20likely%20to%20spread%20spills%20around%20than%20the%20spinning%20circular%20pads.%20It%20also%20slides%20right%20to%20achieve%20wider%20coverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20applied%20jelly%2C%20soda%2C%20and%20maple%20syrup%20to%20my%20hardwood%20floor%20and%20let%20it%20settle%20for%20a%20bit%2C%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20fully%20removed%20the%20mess%20in%20one%20pass.%20There%20was%20a%20slight%20stickiness%20left%20behind%20in%20one%20area.%20This%20is%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20Roborock%20Saros%2020%2C%20which%20left%20a%20much%20stickier%20feel%20over%20the%20whole%20test%20area.%20With%20a%20second%20pass%2C%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20removed%20the%20tacky%20residue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20good%20as%20the%20roller%20brush%20mopping%20performed%2C%20there%20are%20a%20few%20limitations%20around%20carpets.%20It%20It%20also%20doesn't%20have%20a%20cover%20to%20block%20its%20mop%2C%20and%20as%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai's%20mop%20can%20only%20raise%200.4%20inches%2C%20it%20could%20still%20come%20into%20contact%20with%20rugs.%20I%20didn't%20notice%20any%20wet%20spots%20or%20issues%20on%20my%20rugs%2C%20but%20it%20definitely%20touched%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%222d3d3675-6afc-4c03-b287-59ef64fe7f16%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Obstacle%20avoidance%5C%22%3EIts%20smarter%20navigation%20is%20a%20huge%20improvement%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dyson%20robot%20avoiding%20fake%20poop%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0766e9ecd7cc1332bb03ba%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dyson%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20successfully%20avoided%20our%20fake%20poop.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20mopping%2C%20Dyson%20has%20hinged%20this%20product's%20identity%20on%20its%20vision%20%E2%80%94%20being%20able%20to%20%26quot%3Bspot%26quot%3B%20stains.%20For%20the%20most%20part%2C%20that%20bet%20has%20turned%20out%20well.%20The%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20mapped%20my%20rooms%20quickly%20and%20efficiently.%20It%20shows%20the%20robot%20in%20the%20app%20in%20real%20time%20and%20can%20perform%20targeted%20spot%20cleaning.%20It%20also%20means%20that%20it%20saw%20objects%20in%20its%20way%20and%20avoided%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20robot%20was%20able%20to%20completely%20avoid%20different-sized%2C%20shaped%2C%20colored%20faux%20poop%20in%20the%20kitchen.%20The%20mobile%20app%20showed%20how%20it%20went%20around%20two%20areas%20in%20perfect%20circles.%20It%20also%20successfully%20cleared%20a%20USB%20cable.%20Beyond%20purposeful%20tests%2C%20I%20saw%20it%20avoid%20wires%20and%20cables%20under%20a%20couch.%20It%20was%20also%20gentle%20on%20furniture%20legs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDyson%20touts%20that%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20will%20continue%20to%20revisit%20stains%20and%20messes%20it%20spots%20on%20the%20floor%20until%20it%20thinks%20they're%20gone.%20I%20didn't%20see%20much%20of%20this.%20The%20app%20didn't%20reflect%20this%20either.%20The%20robot%20labeled%20many%20objects%20it%20avoided%2C%20but%20only%20one%20or%20two%20mess%20spots%20it%20re-cleaned%20more%20than%20once.%20Some%20of%20my%20dedicated%20tests%20could%20have%20used%20an%20automatic%2C%20second%20pass%20as%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22be04fe7c-6905-453d-88d7-d45d4c8b9dea%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Maintenance%5C%22%3EThe%20all-in-one%20dock%20is%20pure%20Dyson%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225712%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22dyson%20robot%20dust%20station%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0766e9abc4e9d88574a923%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20transparent%20dustbin%20that%20Dyson%20made%20popular%20for%20vacuums%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20base%20station%2C%20which%20makes%20it%20easy%20to%20monitor%20when%20it's%20full.%3Cp%3ETyler%20Hayes%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EOverall%2C%20the%20dock's%20functionality%20is%20great.%20I%20particularly%20love%20the%20clear%2C%20bagless%20canister.%20This%20is%20a%20Dyson%20staple%2C%20and%20it's%20great%20in%20this%20context%20too.%20Nearly%20all%20robot%20vacuums%20hide%20a%20dust%20bag%20inside%20the%20dock%2C%20and%20it's%20impossible%20to%20know%20when%20to%20empty%20it.%20Most%20people%20probably%20either%20never%20empty%20it%20or%20empty%20it%20too%20often.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20some%20may%20not%20be%20too%20keen%20about%20seeing%20the%20collected%20dirt%20on%20display%2C%20with%20the%20clear%20canister%2C%20it's%20very%20easy%20to%20know%20when%20maintenance%20is%20required.%20The%20company%20says%20it%20can%20hold%20100%20days'%20worth%20of%20dirt.%20Based%20on%20how%20empty%20it%20still%20appears%20after%20collecting%20lots%20of%20dust%2C%20cereal%2C%20rice%2C%20and%20other%20debris%2C%20I%20believe%20it.%20Of%20course%2C%20depending%20on%20your%20general%20messiness%2C%20your%20results%20may%20differ.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wish%20the%20freshwater%20container%20were%20clear%2C%20as%20that%20could%20alleviate%20any%20surprise%20notifications%20that%20the%20mopping%20has%20stopped%20until%20it%20can%20be%20refilled.%20For%20obvious%20reasons%2C%20I%20don't%20need%20to%20see%20inside%20the%20dirty%20water%20container.%20A%20word%20of%20warning.%20You%20will%20want%20to%20buy%20the%20%3Ca%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D6ee67df7912bafaad3f272de28c9d7e986d14d7ccb77c1af0de54f89e009af0c%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.dyson.com%252Ffloor-cleaners%252Fcleaning-solutions%252F02-probiotic%252F500ml%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecleaning%20solution%3C%2Fa%3E%20because%2C%20without%20it%2C%20I%20noticed%20a%20smelly%20odor%20when%20emptying%20the%20dirty%20water%20tank.%20Thankfully%2C%20it%20was%20only%20present%20when%20opening%20that%20reservoir.%20When%20the%20brush%20is%20heat-drying%20in%20the%20dock%2C%20the%20brush%20will%20rotate%20to%20keep%20mold%20and%20bad%20smells%20away%20in%20that%20area.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20robot%20cleaned%20well%2C%20the%20robot%20and%20docking%20station%20did%20end%20up%20quite%20messy%20after%20all%20the%20tests.%20While%20routine%20crumb%20cleaning%20and%20not%20mopping%20food%20spills%20will%20make%20maintenance%20much%20less%20frequent%2C%20you%20will%20still%20need%20to%20brush%20off%20the%20dock%20and%20inspect%20under%20the%20robot%20from%20time%20to%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20love%20to%20see%20these%20cleaning%20companies%20develop%20a%20dock-cleaning%20mode%20where%20the%20robot%20spends%20three%20to%20five%20minutes%20sucking%20up%20crumbs%20on%20and%20around%20the%20station.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22972ceb22-6f59-4957-9953-fd84b3e8f54c%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22Battery%20and%20noise%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EBattery%20life%20was%20fine%3B%20noise%20was%20harder%20to%20ignore%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20robot%20vacuums%20gained%20charging%20docks%20with%20self-emptying%20capabilities%2C%20the%20idea%20of%20battery%20life%20became%20a%20little%20moot%2C%20and%20they%20can%20easily%20recharge%20and%20resume%20the%20job%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EStill%2C%20the%20Dyson%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20advertises%20200%20minutes%20of%20runtime%20in%20Quiet%20mode.%20Even%20in%20the%20more%20powerful%20modes%2C%20that%20should%20be%20plenty%20of%20power%20to%20wash%20and%20vacuum%20an%20average-size%20suburban%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20app%20estimated%20my%20~650-square-foot%20downstairs%20would%20take%20about%20108%20minutes%20with%20no%20charging%20stops.%20It%20did%20need%20to%20refill%20the%20water%20at%20one%20point%2C%20but%20that%20was%20quick%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoise%20was%20more%20noticeable.%20The%20robot%20was%20loud%20while%20docking%2C%20refilling%2C%20emptying%20dirty%20water%2C%20and%20moving%20its%20internal%20mechanisms.%20I%20measured%20more%20than%2070%20decibels%20from%20a%20couple%20of%20feet%20away%20while%20it%20serviced%20itself%20at%20the%20dock.%20Quiet%20mode%20was%20much%20more%20tolerable%20for%20routine%20cleaning%2C%20but%20this%20is%20not%20the%20most%20discreet%20robot%20vacuum%20I've%20tested..%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22880429de-93b4-4bb8-bf10-de9755063d08%5C%22%20data-toc-label%3D%5C%22What%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%5C%22%3EWhat%20are%20your%20alternatives%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20the%20Spot%2BScrub%20Ai%20heavily%20focuses%20on%20mopping%2C%20this%20machine%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20for%20people%20with%20all%20carpet.%20Instead%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Dd6ab8427ebf561949858b5543e4b0e7893725393e7d3f1f7d4bf64ca8bd26886%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FDyson-360-Vis-Robot-Vacuum%252Fdp%252FB0CT95LTCJ%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDyson's%20360%20Vis%20Nav%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20the%20one%20whose%20whole%20identity%20is%20carpeting.%20While%20I%20wouldn't%20recommend%20most%20people%20go%20this%20route%2C%20it%20has%20been%20on%20sale%20for%20well%20under%20%24500%2C%20as%20low%20as%20%24280.%20For%20a%20sub%20%24300%20price%2C%20it's%20a%20much%20better%20value%20than%20when%20it%20sold%20for%20%24999%20and%20is%20at%20least%20worth%20considering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20most%20other%20%241%2C000%2B%20products%20on%20our%20best%20robot%20vacuum%20and%20mops%20list%20are%20worthy%20considerations%2C%20not%20all%20use%20the%20single-roller%20brush-style%20mop.%20In%20that%20case%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3Df9009b747fab28231a6e8c7cbed64978c8b1d01876a90a5551333bcbe6ccb953%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.com%252FNARWAL-Self-Cleaning-Recognition-Self-Emptying-Tangle-Free%252Fdp%252FB0GFW4J291%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENarwal%20Flow%202%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20a%20fairly%20direct%20competitor%20with%20the%20same%20mopping%20style%20or%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3Fh%3D2dab46d458f6a9cb05b75993b653683c3ecb312e523624998d781bfbbd5ac6b0%26postID%3D6a0752dfea9599c045f3885b%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fhome%252Fdyson-spot-scrub-ai-robot-vacuum-review%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.amazon.c