%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20BUSINESS%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Meta%20layoffs%3A%20Employees%20told%20to%20work%20from%20home%20as%20countdown%20begins%20for%204%20am%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779184111000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-131196154%2Cimgsize-75574.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Ftechnology%2Ftech-news%2Fmeta-layoffs-employees-told-to-work-from-home-as-countdown-begins-for-4am-emails-leaked-memo-from-hr-chief-says-were-now-at-the-stage-where%2Farticleshow%2F131196008.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Meta%20is%20laying%20off%20around%208%2C000%20employees%20on%20Wednesday%2C%20May%2020%2C%20with%20notification%20emails%20going%20out%20in%20three%20regional%20waves%20starting%20at%204%20AM%20local%20time.%20A%20leaked%20memo%20from%20HR%20chief%20Janelle%20Gale%20tells%20North%20American%20staff%20to%20work%20from%20home%20as%20the%20cuts%20roll%20out.%20Meanwhile%2C%207%2C000%20workers%20are%20being%20reassigned%20to%20four%20new%20AI-focused%20organisations%20as%20Mark%20Zuckerberg%20restructures%20Meta%20around%20flatter%20teams%2C%20fewer%20managers%2C%20and%20a%20%24145%20billion%20AI%20bet.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20TECH%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22I%20got%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20within%2090%20days%20of%20getting%20laid%20off%20from%20AWS.%20I%20started%20preparing%20well%20beforehand.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Charles%20Broomfield%20outside%20Amazon%20office%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b36f0abc4e9d88574b0dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221536%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECharles%20Broomfield's%20last%20day%20at%20Amazon%20Web%20Services%3Cp%3ECharles%20Broomfield%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ECharles%20Broomfield%20was%20cut%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faws%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAWS%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Google%20within%2090%20days.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHe%20said%20he%20got%20referrals%20for%2026%20roles%20when%20job%20hunting%2C%20and%20six%20turned%20into%20interviews.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBroomfield%20said%20financial%20planning%20and%20networking%20helped%20him%20stay%20calm%20after%20getting%20laid%20off.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20as-told-to%20essay%20is%20based%20on%20a%20conversation%20with%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fcharles-broomfield%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ECharles%20Broomfield%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%2C%20a%2025-year-old%20engineering%20analyst%20at%20Google%2C%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20His%20employment%20and%20identity%20have%20been%20confirmed%20by%20Business%20Insider.%20This%20story%20has%20been%20edited%20for%20length%20and%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20graduated%20from%20a%20tiny%20liberal%20arts%20college%20called%20Knox%20College.%20The%20downside%20is%20to%20that%20that%20there%20is%20a%20much%20smaller%20alumni%20network.%20The%20benefit%20is%20that%20I%20suspect%20the%20likelihood%20of%20them%20being%20willing%20to%20help%20out%20is%20much%20higher.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20was%20a%20computer%20science%20tutor%20there.%20That%20ended%20up%20being%20an%20advantage%20because%20I%20got%20to%20work%20with%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20who%20are%20now%20at%20great%20companies%20and%20were%20willing%20to%20help%20me%20out.%20I%20started%20working%20at%20a%20government%20research%20company%20after%20college%2C%20and%20went%20over%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon%3C%2Fa%3E%20Web%20Services%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202025.%20Then%2C%20in%20late%20January%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-new-layoffs-restructuring-continues-cultural-reset-andy-jassy-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EI%20got%20laid%20off%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20April%2C%20I%20accepted%20an%20offer%20for%20a%20job%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2269547869-a9d5-47e4-bd1a-1b636ee73801%5C%22%3EI%20treated%20my%20job%20hunt%20like%20a%20job%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20I%20joined%20Amazon%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-ceo-says-generative-ai-expect-job-cuts-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAndy%20Jassy%20had%20made%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20how%20Amazon%20would%20have%20fewer%20people%20in%20the%20future%20because%20of%20AI.%20I%20became%20increasingly%20nervous%20that%20my%20team%20wasn't%20aligned%20with%20the%20strategy.%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20started%20applying%20on%20January%2024%2C%20but%20I%20was%20given%20notice%20of%20my%20layoff%20a%20few%20days%20later.%20I%20was%20pretty%20confident%20that%20my%20team%20would%20be%20affected%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20leave%20before%20getting%2090%20days'%20notice%20and%20severance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20found%20it%20really%20hard%20to%20go%20from%20working%20at%20a%20company%20with%20a%20pretty%20famous%20work%20culture%2C%20like%20AWS%2C%20to%20a%20complete%20hard%20stop.%20So%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frecent-company-layoffs-laying-off-workers-2026%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ewhen%20I%20was%20laid%20off%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20I%20figured%20I'd%20put%20all%20my%20energy%20into%20something%20productive.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20definitely%20nice%20to%20get%20an%20extra%20hour%20or%20so%20of%20sleep%2C%20but%20I%20tried%20to%20maintain%20a%20sense%20of%20structure%20during%20my%20job%20hunt.%20I'd%20usually%20spend%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20day%20reaching%20out%20to%20folks%20and%20finding%20positions.%20I%20wasn't%20going%20through%20every%20job%20posting%20and%20hitting%20apply%20because%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20interview%20for%20something%20I'm%20not%20genuinely%20excited%20about.%20I%20was%20picky.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDoing%20eight%20straight%20hours%20of%20applications%20is%20pretty%20brutal%2C%20so%20I'd%20usually%20work%20out%20or%20cook%20to%20break%20things%20up%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20the%20day.%20Then%20I%20would%20spend%20another%20three-%20or%20four-hour%20stretch%20in%20the%20evening%20tailoring%20applications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22236a85da-c7f6-474d-a603-c5382755cba7%5C%22%3EReferrals%20make%20a%20huge%20difference%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20being%20laid%20off%20from%20AWS%2C%20I%20applied%20to%2042%20positions%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E26%20of%20which%20I%20had%20referrals%20for%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20interviewed%20for%20six%20of%20those%20jobs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20previous%20colleague%20reached%20out%20and%20encouraged%20me%20to%20apply%20to%20Google.%20I%20applied%20to%20three%20positions%2C%20and%20was%20quickly%20rejected%20from%20the%20two%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20most%20likely%20to%20land.%20But%20about%20a%20week%20after%20I%20applied%2C%20the%20recruiter%20for%20the%20third%20position%20reached%20out.%20The%20next%20week%2C%20I%20passed%20the%20technical%20screen.%20Then%20I%20had%20three%20interviews%20over%20the%20next%20two%20weeks%20and%20received%20an%20offer%20a%20few%20days%20after%20my%20final%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20get%20referrals%20wrong.%20I%20did%20a%20lot%20of%20LinkedIn%20outreach%2C%20but%20it%20was%20really%20ineffective.%20I%20always%20start%20with%20my%20warmest%20audience.%20So%20I%20begin%20with%20friends%2C%20and%20then%20I%20expand.%20I%20even%20consider%20somebody%20who%20went%20to%20my%20college%20a%20little%20warm%2C%20because%20I%20went%20to%20a%20tiny%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20I've%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Famazon-job-cuts-layoffs-cost-saving-measure-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eworked%20at%20companies%20that%20did%20large%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20people%20I%20worked%20with%20ended%20up%20at%20big%20companies%2C%20and%20that%20helped%20with%20referrals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYour%20network%20isn't%20just%20the%20people%20you%20talk%20to%20every%20day.%20It%20can%20be%20anyone%20that%20you've%20met%20who%20you've%20made%20a%20positive%20impression%20on.%20I%20have%20a%20list%20of%20people%20that%20I%20reach%20out%20to%20whenever%20I%20have%20a%20major%20career%20update%2C%20but%20there's%20many%20other%20people%20who%20I%20only%20stay%20in%20touch%20with%20through%20social%20media.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELeaving%20a%20friendly%20or%20supportive%20comment%20can%20go%20way%20further%20than%20people%20realize.%20The%20best%20connections%20are%20sometimes%20friends%20of%20friends%20or%20random%20acquaintances%2C%20not%20your%20closest%20friends%20or%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22844abc63-463a-4a7a-b74c-948d4ce53816%5C%22%3ESavings%20gave%20me%20peace%20of%20mind%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20super%20passionate%20about%20early%20retirement%2C%20frugality%2C%20and%20building%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2F%40CharlesBroomfieldOfficial%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20freedom%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20save%20everything%20I%20can%2C%20and%20I've%20been%20doing%20that%20since%20college.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20craziness%20over%20the%20last%20year%20made%20me%20realize%20how%20grateful%20I%20was%20for%20those%20savings%20because%20of%20the%20peace%20of%20mind%20and%20flexibility%20it%20gave%20me.%20I%20really%20feel%20for%20people%20who%20are%20counting%20on%20their%20next%20few%20paychecks%2C%20or%20for%20folks%20whose%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwall-street-h-1b-petitions-fall-after-trump-visa-crackdown-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Evisas%20are%20tied%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20their%20work.%20It's%20harder%20to%20operate%20when%20you're%20stressed.%20Desperation%20doesn't%20help.%20So%20my%20buffer%20definitely%20made%20me%20more%20relaxed.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENetworks%20are%20more%20powerful%20than%20job%20boards%2C%20but%20I%20suggest%20people%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetworking-important-new-job-economy-ai-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20building%20their%20networks%3C%2Fa%3E%20now%20rather%20than%20wait%20until%20they%20need%20help.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-landed-job-within-90-days-of-aws-layoff-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779183901000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b36f0abc4e9d88574b0dd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-employee-landed-job-within-90-days-of-aws-layoff-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Charles%20Broomfield%20said%20he%20got%20referrals%20for%2026%20roles%20when%20job%20hunting%2C%20and%20six%20turned%20into%20interviews.%20He%20landed%20a%20job%20at%20Google.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22aaltchek%40insider.com%20(Ana%20Altchek)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tripura%20Security%20Forces%20Couple%20Arrested%20After%20Cash%20Video%20Goes%20Viral%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Couple%20serving%20in%20Tripura%20security%20forces%20detained%20following%20viral%20currency%20video.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779183711000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-05%2F3iskudak_tripura-woman-cop-cash_625x300_19_May_26.jpg%3