195431.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20CEO%20behind%20Grand%20Theft%20Auto%20says%20he's%20pro%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20but%20the%20technology%20can't%20make%20an%20original%20hit%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Strauss%20Zelnick%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Take-Two%20Interactive%2C%20sits%20in%20an%20armchair%20onstage.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b3da6abc4e9d88574b129%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EStrauss%20Zelnick%20is%20%26quot%3Ball%20in%26quot%3B%20on%20using%20AI.%20He%20is%20skeptical%20that%20it%20can%20make%20a%20hit%20video%20game.%3Cp%3EIMF%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3ETake-Two's%20CEO%20said%20AI%20is%20useful%20for%20speeding%20up%20parts%20of%20video-game%20development.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBut%20he%20said%20the%20tool%20isn't%20great%20at%20manufacturing%20cultural%20hits%20%E2%80%94%20like%20the%20studio's%20blockbuster%20%26quot%3BGTA5.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20Take-Two%20CEO%20pushed%20back%20on%20fears%20that%20AI%20will%20replace%20popular%20game%20studios.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftake-two-ceo-ai-better-paying-video-game-jobs-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETake-Two%20Interactive%20CEO%20Strauss%20Zelnick%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he's%20embracing%20AI%20to%20help%20make%20video%20games%20more%20efficiently.%20He%20just%20doesn't%20think%20the%20technology%20can%20create%20the%20next%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Theft%20Auto%26quot%3B%20from%20scratch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20David%20Senra's%20podcast%2C%20posted%20on%20Sunday%2C%20Zelnick%20said%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Ball%20in%26quot%3B%20on%20AI%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20pushed%20back%20on%20the%20idea%20that%20it%20can%20create%20the%20originality%20and%20surprise%20needed%20to%20create%20a%20blockbuster%20hit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRemember%20what%20AI%20is%2C%20despite%20the%20fact%20that%20there%20are%20people%20in%20Silicon%20Valley%20who%20don't%20want%20you%20to%20believe%20this%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20big%20data%20sets%2C%20lots%20of%20compute%2C%20and%20a%20large%20language%20model%20mushed%20together.%20That's%20what%20they%20are.%20So%2C%20data%20sets%20by%20their%20very%20nature%20are%20backward-looking.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETake-Two's%20Rockstar%20Games%20label%20makes%20the%20hugely%20popular%20%26quot%3BGrand%20Theft%20Auto%26quot%3B%20series.%20The%20open-world%20crime%20game's%20fifth%20installment%20%E2%80%94%20which%20features%20robberies%2C%20police%20chases%2C%20satire%2C%20violence%2C%20and%2C%20yes%2C%20auto%20theft%20%E2%80%94%20was%20a%20massive%20success%2C%20selling%20more%20than%20200%20million%20global%20copies%20since%20its%202013%20debut.%20The%20twice-delayed%20%26quot%3B%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrand-theft-auto-6-delayed-2026-rockstar-games-gta-2025-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGrand%20Theft%20Auto%20VI%3C%2Fa%3E%26quot%3B%20is%20among%20the%20most%20anticipated%20games%20in%20entertainment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EZelnick%20said%20AI%20could%20create%20another%20GTA%20lookalike%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bclones%20don't%20sell%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Senra.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAI%20so%20far%20is%20really%20great%20at%20asset%20creation%2C%20but%20hit%20creation%20isn't%20asset%20creation%2C%26quot%3B%20Zelnick%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20comments%20cut%20against%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbill-gurley-ai-dealmaking-meta-amd-saaspocalypse-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecommon%20investor%20fear%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20that%20AI%20tools%20could%20lower%20the%20barrier%20to%20game%20creation%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-the-music-industry-is-changing-its-tune-on-ai-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethreaten%20established%20publishers%3C%2Fa%3E%20like%20Take-Two.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnyone%20can%20make%20a%20video%20game%20last%20week%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BAnyone%20could%20make%20a%20video%20game%20five%20years%20ago.%20The%20technology%20is%20readily%20available.%20It's%20commoditized.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20Zelnick%20has%20tried%20to%20separate%20AI%20productivity%20gains%20from%20creating%20culture-shaping%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrauss-zelnick-take-two-ceo-grand-theft-auto-gta-6-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EZelnick%20explained%20his%20AI%20stance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20a%20recent%20interview%20with%20Business%20Insider's%20Sarah%20Needleman.%20He%20said%20Take-Two%20employees%20are%20encouraged%20to%20use%20tools%20such%20as%20Anthropic's%20Claude%20and%20Google's%20Gemini.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20he%20also%20said%20those%20gains%20do%20not%20necessarily%20mean%20blockbuster%20games%20will%20become%20cheaper%20or%20faster%20to%20make%2C%20because%20easier%20tools%20tend%20to%20raise%20creative%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEveryone%20understands%20this%20creates%20more%20work%2C%20not%20less%20work%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you%20make%20certain%20things%20easier%2C%20your%20appetite%20gets%20greater.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20declined%20to%20comment%20beyond%20Zelnick's%20remarks%20on%20the%20podcast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftake-two-ceo-ai-gta6-original-work-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779182941000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b439c94eb4c909fb2d8a3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftake-two-ceo-ai-gta6-original-work-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Take-Two%20CEO%20Strauss%20Zelnick%20says%20AI%20can%20make%20video-game%20development%20more%20efficient%2C%20but%20