g%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia's%20Jonathan%20Ross%20said%20AI%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20may%20be%20preferred%20by%20AI%20screening%20tools%20in%20hiring.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%3C%2Fa%3E's%20Jonathan%20Ross%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20likes%20to%20use%20AI.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EResearch%20shows%20that%20AI%20screening%20tools%20may%20favor%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20generated%20by%20the%20same%20AI%20models%20they%20use.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ERoss%20said%20that%20applicants%20may%20need%20multiple%20AI-tailored%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20to%20maximize%20their%20chances.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20Chief%20Software%20Architect%20said%20job%20seekers%20could%20benefit%20from%20using%20the%20same%20AI%20model%20that%20recruiters%20use.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20at%20the%20Sohn%20Investment%20Conference%202026%2C%20Jonathan%20Ross%2C%20the%20AI%20hardware%20architect%20who%20previously%20helped%20invent%20Google's%20TPU%20chip%2C%20said%20that%20%26quot%3BAI%20likes%20to%20use%20AI%26quot%3B%20and%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epointed%20to%20emerging%20research%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-ai-is-changing-job-applications-and-hiring-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI%20hiring%20systems%3C%2Fa%3E%20may%20favor%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20generated%20by%20their%20own%20underlying%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20did%20a%20study%20and%20showed%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbi-today-sunday-newsletter-no-more-resumes-show-up-instead-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Er%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20generated%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20one%20LLM%20are%20preferred%20by%20that%20same%20LLM%20over%20the%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20from%20the%20other%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20told%20John%20Yetimoglu%2C%20the%20CIO%20of%20Infinitum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20recruiters%20are%20now%20using%20LLM%20to%20determine%20who%20to%20interview%2C%20but%20you%20got%20to%20figure%20out%20which%20LLM%20the%20recruiter's%20using%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20said%20that%20applicants%20may%20need%20multiple%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhiring-managers-arent-reading-resumes-slop-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAI-tailored%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20maximize%20their%20chances%20of%20getting%20through%20automated%20screening%20systems.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSo%2C%20you%20should%20build%20one%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9%20with%20Claude%20or%20Opus%204.7%20and%20one%20with%20ChatGPT%2C%20and%20you'll%20have%20the%20highest%20probability%20of%20being%20selected%2C%20basically%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20appeared%20to%20be%20referring%20to%20a%20recent%20academic%20paper%20titled%20%26quot%3BAI%20Self-preferencing%20in%20Algorithmic%20Hiring%2C%26quot%3B%20published%20in%20a%20late%202025%20edition%20of%20%26quot%3BProceedings%20of%20the%20AAAI%2FACM%20Conference%20on%20AI%2C%20Ethics%2C%20and%20Society%2C%26quot%3B%C2%A0by%20researchers%20Jiannan%20Xu%2C%20Gujie%20Li%2C%20and%20Jane%20Yi%20Jiang.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20researchers%20tested%20more%20than%202%2C200%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20across%2024%20occupations%20and%20found%20that%20applicants%20using%20the%20same%20AI%20model%20as%20the%20evaluator%20were%20between%2023%25%20and%2060%25%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20shortlisted%20than%20candidates%20submitting%20human-written%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20with%20similar%20qualifications.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20comments%20come%20as%20AI-powered%20hiring%20tools%20are%20quickly%20spreading%20through%20corporate%20recruiting%20departments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%202025%20Resume.org%20survey%20of%20nearly%201%2C400%20US%20workers%20familiar%20with%20their%20companies'%20hiring%20practices%20found%20that%2057%25%20of%20companies%20were%20already%20using%20AI%20in%20hiring%20workflows.%20Among%20those%20employers%2C%2079%25%20said%20they%20use%20AI%20to%20review%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%2C%20while%2074%25%20said%20AI%20systems%20could%20reject%20candidates%20without%20human%20review.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rapid%20adoption%20of%20AI%20screening%20tools%20has%20also%20sparked%20growing%20concerns%20about%20bias%20and%20false%20negatives%20in%20hiring.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBusiness%20Insider%20recently%20reported%20that%20an%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fit-pro-reached-out-after-receiving-job-rejection-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EIT%20worker%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20was%20rejected%20for%20a%20role%20six%20minutes%20after%20applying%2C%20and%20suspected%20that%20AI%20software%20had%20automatically%20screened%20him%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-exec-ai-likes-to-use-ai-it-impacts-resumes-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779182101000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b8fe4abc4e9d88574b3e8%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-exec-ai-likes-to-use-ai-it-impacts-resumes-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22AI%20r%C3%A9sum%C3%A9s%20might%20be%20favored%20by%20AI%20hiring%20systems%2C%20especially%20if%20you%20use%20the%20same%20LLM%20model%20as%20the%20recruiters%2C%20said%20Nvidia's%20Jonathan%20Ross.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22katherineli%40insider.com%20(Katherine%20Li)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A10%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22'CM%20Adhikari%20promised%20...'%3A%20Jahangir%20Khan%20exits%20Falta%20repoll%3B%20TMC%20says%20'succumbed%20to%20pressure'%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779181823000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A