.com%2Fentertainment%2Fenglish%2Fhollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-white-lotus-season-4-begins-filming-at-cannes-film-festival-watch%2Farticleshow%2F131191685.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F131191685.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EFilming%20for%20'The%20White%20Lotus'%20Season%204%20has%20commenced%20in%20France%2C%20with%20cast%20members%20spotted%20at%20the%20Cannes%20Film%20Festival.%20The%20upcoming%20season%2C%20set%20against%20the%20glamorous%20backdrop%20of%20the%20French%20Riviera%2C%20will%20reportedly%20explore%20celebrity%20culture.%20Initially%20planned%20as%20a%20multi-country%20European%20tour%2C%20creator%20Mike%20White%20decided%20to%20focus%20solely%20on%20France%20after%20a%20captivating%20experience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A98%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Audemars%20Piguet%20is%20walking%20a%20fine%20line%20between%20cheapening%20its%20brand%20and%20riding%20a%20lucrative%20hype%20train%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225938%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Bioceramic%20Royal%20Pop%20Collection%20is%20seen%20on%20display%20in%20a%20shop%20window%20of%20Swatch%20store%20in%20Krakow%2C%20Poland%20on%20May%2018th%2C%202026%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0bf821abc4e9d88574b4b6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223961%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAudemars%20Piguet%20launched%20a%20pocket%20watch%20collection%20with%20Swatch%2C%20and%20fans%20lost%20it.%3Cp%3EBeata%20Zawrzel%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20launch%20of%20the%20Audemars%20Piguet%20x%20Swatch%20collection%20unraveled%20into%20global%20chaos%20on%20Saturday.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EFans%20had%20to%20endure%20long%20queues%2C%20fistfights%2C%20and%20even%20tear%20gas%20deployment%20to%20cop%20the%20%24400%20watches.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EBrand%20and%20watch%20experts%20said%20Audemars%20Piguet%20was%20walking%20a%20fine%20line%20with%20the%20tumult.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EZerxes%20Wadia's%20Saturday%20morning%20started%20feeling%20like%20a%20side%20quest%20gone%20horribly%20wrong%20when%20he%20realized%20he%20was%20competing%20with%20a%20horde%20of%20relentless%20people%2C%20all%20angling%20for%20a%20chance%20to%20cop%20a%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20content%20creator%20arrived%20at%20the%20Phoenix%20Palladium%20mall%20in%20Mumbai%20at%205%20a.m.%20to%20buy%20a%20piece%20from%20the%20viral%20Audemars%20Piguet%20and%20Swatch%20%26quot%3BRoyal%20Pop%26quot%3B%20pocket%20watch%20collection.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20found%20himself%20shoulder-to-shoulder%20with%20hundreds%20of%20people%20who%20had%20the%20same%20idea%2C%20all%20packed%20into%20a%20seemingly%20endless%20queue%20outside%20the%20Swatch%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rush%20to%20get%20one%20of%20the%20eight%20colorful%20pocket%20watches%2C%20priced%20around%20%24400%20each%2C%20on%20May%2016%20turned%20really%20ugly%2C%20really%20fast.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThings%20quickly%20took%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fswatch-audemars-piguet-watch-fans-camp-in-times-square-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Echaotic%20turn%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20around%208%3A30%20a.m.%2C%20when%20he%20said%20people%20started%20jumping%20barricades%2C%20running%20in%2C%20and%20breaking%20a%20security%20checkpoint.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fembed.js%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FDYYwuUwIbYO%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3C