0target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esnaking%20queues%3C%2Fa%3E%20outside%20Swatch%20stores%20all%20around%20the%20world%2C%20from%20Singapore%20to%20New%20York%20City.%20Although%20the%20watch%20companies%20said%20the%20collection%20would%20remain%20available%20for%20%26quot%3Bseveral%20months%2C%26quot%3B%20fans%20treated%20it%20like%20a%20limited-edition%20drop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESwatch%20tried%20to%20control%20the%20chaos%2C%20saying%20in%20a%20press%20release%20that%20queues%20of%20more%20than%2050%20people%20would%20not%20be%20allowed%20and%20that%20sales%20may%20need%20to%20be%20paused.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20ensure%20the%20safety%20of%20both%20our%20customers%20and%20our%20staff%20in%20Swatch%20stores%2C%20we%20kindly%20ask%20you%20not%20to%20rush%20to%20our%20stores%20in%20large%20numbers%20to%20acquire%20this%20product%2C%26quot%3B%20Swatch%20said%20after%20the%20launch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAn%20Audemars%20Piguet%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20given%20the%20%26quot%3Bscale%20of%20public%20turnout%20observed%20in%20certain%20markets%2C%26quot%3B%20Swatch%20had%20to%20delay%20the%20launch%20for%20safety%20reasons.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Swatch%20spokesperson%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%2C%20out%20of%20a%20total%20of%20220%20stores%20where%20the%20collection%20was%20launched%2C%20problems%20occurred%20at%20around%2020%20stores%20because%20%26quot%3Bqueues%20of%20interested%20customers%20were%20exceptionally%20long%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20some%20shopping%20malls%20were%20unable%20to%20handle%20the%20turnout.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274af35df-2231-4c2c-8f34-2ab372bf270a%5C%22%3EA%20collab%20primed%20for%20younger%20customers%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223887%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Swatch%20x%20Audemars%20Piguet%20Royal%20Pop%20watches%20on%20display%20at%20a%20Swatch%20Group%20AG%20store%20in%20Times%20Square%20in%20New%20York%2C%20US%2C%20on%20Thursday%2C%20May%2014%2C%202026.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0bf8aaecd7cc1332bb0f6a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222591%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20collection%20is%20geared%20toward%20a%20young%2C%20aspirational%20consumer%20base.%3Cp%3EBloomberg%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collaboration%20was%20curated%20for%20a%20younger%2C%20more%20fun-loving%2C%20and%20less%20affluent%20customer%20base.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompared%20to%20Audemars%20Piguet's%20most%20popular%20watches%20%E2%80%94%20its%20Royal%20Oak%20line%20goes%20for%20more%20than%20%2440%2C000%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0the%20%26quot%3BRoyal%20Pop%26quot%3B%20pocket%20watch%20collection%20rests%20snugly%20in%20the%20aspirational%20luxury%20category.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20watches%20feature%20the%20octagonal%20face%20belonging%20to%20Audemars%20Piguet's%20iconic%20%26quot%3BRoyal%20Oak%26quot%3B%20watch%2C%20but%20with%20funky%20color%20combinations%20like%20yellow%20and%20pink%2C%20and%20orange%20and%20blue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThey%20come%20attached%20to%20a%20leather%20lanyard%2C%20making%20it%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-bag-cute-charms-origins-of-bag-charm-cult-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebag%20charm%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20a%20Gen%20Z-favorite%20accessory.%20Jade%20Rasif%2C%20a%20Singaporean%20DJ%20and%20YouTuber%2C%20posted%20a%20TikTok%20swapping%20out%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flabubu-pop-mart-popularity-decline-overreliance-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPop%20Mart's%20viral%20Labubu%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20her%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftelltale-signs-of-fake-birkin-according-to-vintage-luxury-expert-2024-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EHerm%C3%A8s%20Birkin%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20a%20black%20%26quot%3BRoyal%20Pop%26quot%3B%20pocket%20watch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMolly%20Frampton%2C%20a%20strategy%20director%20at%20New%20York-based%20brand%20consultancy%20Interbrand%2C%20said%20the%20collaboration%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bbold%20opportunity%20for%20both%20brands%3A%20to%20stretch%2C%20expand%2C%20and%20have%20a%20bit%20of%20fun.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20collection%20is%20tailored%20for%20younger%20aspirational%20customers%20who%20are%20aware%20of%20Audemars%20Piguet's%20heritage%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bcould%20not%20fork%20out%20thousands%20of%20pounds%20for%20one%20of%20their%20watches%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Vicky%20Bullen%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20London-based%20branding%20agency%20Coley%20Porter%20Bell.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22293664ae-27a7-42d6-a060-d65a5e848693%5C%22%3ETear%20gas%20doesn't%20scream%20luxury%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228080%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Police%20gather%20outside%20the%20Swatch%20store%20in%20St.%20Davids%20Shopping%20centre%20on%20May%2016%2C%202026%20in%20Cardiff%2C%20Wales.%20Swatch%20are%20today%20releasing%20the%20Swatch%20x%20Audemars%20Piguet%20Royal%20Pop%20pocket%20watch.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0bf92e94eb4c909fb2dbe3%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225387%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20crowds%20triggered%20police%20action%20in%20several%20cities.%3Cp%3EMatthew%20Horwood%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20store%20in%20Paris%2C%20French%20police%20deployed%20tear%20gas%20to%20break%20up%20the%20crowd.%20Fights%20broke%20out%20in%20a%20Milan%20store%20line.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNothing%20says%20'luxury%20horology'%20quite%20like%20police%20dogs%20and%20tear%20gas%2C%20right%3F%26quot%3B%20said%20Eugene%20Tutunikov%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20secondhand%20luxury%20watch%20retailer%20SwissWatchExpo.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhile%20the%20hype%20is%20a%20marketer's%20dream%2C%20getting%20pepper-sprayed%20isn't%20exactly%20the%20premium%20customer%20experience%20anyone%20is%20looking%20for%20when%20trying%20to%20buy%20a%20timepiece%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETutunikov%20said%20selling%20an%20accessible%20watch%20like%2