0and%20Michael%20Nagle%2FBloomberg%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EGoogle%20and%20Blackstone%20announced%20a%20new%20AI%20company%20to%20challenge%20CoreWeave%20and%20Nebius.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20new%20AI%20company%20will%20leverage%20Google's%20TPUs%20to%20offer%20enhanced%20compute%20options%20for%20businesses.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EHere's%20what%20smart%20people%20are%20saying%20about%20the%20new%20deal.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-private-equity-chasing-data-center-opportunity-blackstone-ares-apollo-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle%20and%20Blackstone%3C%2Fa%3E%20are%20launching%20a%20new%20AI%20company%20that%20would%20rival%20cloud%20providers%20like%20CoreWeave%20and%20Nebius.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBlackstone%2C%20the%20world's%20biggest%20asset%20manager%2C%20will%20invest%20%245%20billion%20in%20the%20new%20US-based%20company%20at%20the%20start%2C%20the%20firms%20said%20Monday.%20The%20company%2C%20which%20has%20not%20been%20publicly%20named%2C%20plans%20to%20offer%20data%20center%20capacity%2C%20operations%2C%20and%20Google%20Cloud's%20Tensor%20Processing%20Units%20as%20a%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThomas%20Kurian%2C%20the%20CEO%20of%20Google%20Cloud%2C%20said%20in%20the%20statement%20that%20the%20new%20company%20gives%20organizations%20more%20options%20to%20access%20compute.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20joint%20venture%20with%20Blackstone%20helps%20meet%20growing%20demand%20for%20TPUs%2C%20which%20are%20optimized%20specifically%20for%20efficiency%20and%20performance%20in%20the%20AI%20era%2C%26quot%3B%20Kurian%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere's%20how%20tech%20analysts%20and%20investors%20reacted%20to%20the%20news%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERittenhouse%20Research%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%2C%20Rittenhouse%20Research%2C%20a%20market%20research%20and%20investment%20analysis%20firm%2C%20noted%20that%20most%20major%20neocloud%20providers%20%E2%80%94%20including%20CoreWeave%2C%20Nebius%2C%20Crusoe%2C%20and%20Lambda%20%E2%80%94%20have%20largely%20aligned%20themselves%20with%20Nvidia%20hardware%2C%20creating%20an%20opening%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Falphabet-nvidia-stock-prices-most-valuable-company-googl-nvda-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EGoogle-backed%20TPU%20alternatives%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20firm%20added%20that%20while%20the%20move%20could%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgoogle-new-ai-chips-tpu-inference-training-nvidia-2026-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eincrease%20competition%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20those%20companies%2C%20it's%20ultimately%20a%20strong%20endorsement%20of%20the%20neocloud%20model%20that%20those%20firms%20helped%20establish.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EGilles%20Drieu%2C%20former%20director%20of%20engineering%20at%20Google%3Cp%3EGilles%20Drieu%2C%20the%20chief%20technology%20officer%20at%20ADT%20and%20a%20former%20engineering%20leader%20at%20Google%2C%20said%20Google%20and%20Blackstone's%20new%20TPU-based%20AI%20cloud%20reflects%20several%20major%20shifts%20underway%20in%20the%20AI%20infrastructure%20market.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20an%20X%20post%2C%20he%20said%20that%20hyperscalers%20are%20beginning%20to%20commercialize%20their%20proprietary%20chips%20outside%20their%20own%20cloud%20platforms.%20Meanwhile%2C%20private%20capital%20is%20increasingly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fblackstone-anthropic-hellman-goldman-sachs-ai-joint-venture-consulting-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efunding%20large-scale%20AI%20%3C%2Fa%3Einfrastructure%20projects%20once%20financed%20directly%20by%20Big%20Tech%20companies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrieu%20also%20said%20the%20AI%20stack%20is%20becoming%20more%20vertically%20integrated%2C%20spanning%20chips%2C%20inference%2C%20and%20energy%20infrastructure.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCompute%20is%20starting%20to%20behave%20like%20a%20strategic%20supply%20chain%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote%20on%20X.%3Cbr%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJason%20Kotik%2C%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Rockefeller%20Global%20Investment%20Management%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B'Welcome%20to%20Hell'%20is%20the%20perfect%20way%20to%20put%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Kotik%2C%20an%20equities%20portfolio%20manager%20at%20Rockefeller%20Global.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BGoogle%20and%20Blackstone%20joining%20forces%20means%20every%20other%20AI%20company%20just%20got%20put%20on%20notice%2C%26quot%3B%20Kotik%20said%20on%20X.%20%26quot%3BThe%20big%20players%20are%20consolidating%20power%20fast%2C%20and%20the%20small%20fry%20are%20getting%20squeezed%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmart-people-react-google-blackstone-collab-5-billion-ai-company-2026-5%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779169207000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0bec8eecd7cc1332bb0f5e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsmart-people-react-google-blackstone-collab-5-billion-ai-company-2026-5%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%26quot%3BThe%20small%20fry%20are%20getting%20squeezed%20out%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20one%20equities%20portfolio%20manager.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sgoel%40insider.com%20(Shubhangi%20Goel)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A97%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22SC%20refuses%20to%20change%20verdict%20on%20stray%20dog%20removal%20from%20public%20institutions%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1779169183000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fbsmedia.business-standard.com%2F_media%2Fbs%2Fimg%2Farticle%2F2025-08%2F12%2Fthumb%2Ffitandfill%2F1200X628%2F1754976879-9637.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findia-news%2Fsc-refuses-to-change-verdict-on-stray-dog-re