com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcuba-us-military-action-would-lead-to-a-bloodbath%2Famp_articleshow%2F131190657.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fcuba-us-military-action-would-lead-to-a-bloodbath%2Famp_articleshow%2F131190657.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Russia%20was%20facing%20monthslong%20delays%20in%20anti-jam%20antennas.%20Now%20it's%20putting%20them%20on%20foam%20decoys%20for%20Shaheds.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%226048%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20Gerbera%20is%20seen%20on%20display%20at%20a%20Ukrainain%20booth%20in%202025.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0bd05becd7cc1332bb0f24%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%224024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGerberas%2C%20such%20as%20the%20one%20seen%20here%2C%20are%20typically%20decoys%20for%20Russia's%20version%20of%20the%20Shahed%20attack%20drone.%3Cp%3EDanylo%20Antoniuk%2FUkrinform%2FNurPhoto%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EUkraine%20is%20finding%20advanced%20antennas%20on%20Russia's%20low-priority%20foam%20and%20plywood%20Gerbera%20drones.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20top%20drone%20advisor%20said%20it's%20a%20sign%20Russia%20has%20surged%20production%20of%20the%20anti-jamming%20component.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThat's%20just%20after%20Russia%20was%20facing%20a%20three-to-five-month%20wait%20for%20these%20antennas%20last%20year%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EUkrainian%20troops%20are%20finding%20advanced%20antennas%20with%20stronger%20anti-jamming%20features%20on%20Russian%20decoy%20drones%2C%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20Kremlin%20is%20overcoming%20a%20shortage%20of%20the%20key%20component.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESerhii%20%26quot%3BFlash%26quot%3B%20Beskrestnov%2C%20a%20prominent%20Ukrainian%20drone%20analyst%2C%20posted%20photos%20to%20social%20media%20on%20Wednesday%20of%20a%20downed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgerbera-back-cameras-russia-shahed-drone-war-interceptor-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edelta-wing%20Gerbera%20drone%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%2012-element%20Controlled%20Reception%20Pattern%20Antenna.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BRecently%2C%2012-element%20Kometa%20antennas%20have%20begun%20to%20appear%20on%20the%20Gerberas%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Beskrestnov%2C%20who%20is%20the%20Ukrainian%20defense%20minister's%20advisor%20on%20battle%20drone%20tech.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20this%20is%20a%20sign%20that%20the%20plant%20that%20produces%20Kometa%20has%20increased%20its%20production%20capacity.%20A%20year%20ago%2C%20there%20were%20not%20enough%20Kometas%20even%20for%20KABs%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added%2C%20referring%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-pounds-ukraine-region-40-massive-glide-bombs-one-night-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ERussian%20precision%20glide%20bombs%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThere%20was%20a%20three-to-five-month%20queue%20at%20the%20plant.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%20data-script%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftelegram.org%2Fjs%2Ftelegram-widget.js%3F23%5C%22%20data-styles%3D%5C%22default-width%5C%22%20data-embed-type%3D%5C%22custom%5C%22%20data-type%3D%5C%22embed%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cp%3EAntennas%20with%20more%20elements%20are%20generally%20more%20resistant%20to%20electronic%20warfare%2C%20one%20of%20Ukraine's%20main%20ways%20to%20disrupt%20or%20take%20down%20incoming%20drones.%20More%20basic%20versions%20of%20the%20Kometa%2C%20Russia's%20family%20of%20anti-jamming%20antennas%2C%20have%20four-%20or%20eight-element%20arrays.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20a%20Russian%20Gerbera%20would%20be%20equipped%20with%20a%2012-element%20antenna%20is%20significant.%20Moscow%20typically%20uses%20Gerberas%20as%20decoys%20to%20absorb%20Ukrainian%20air%20defense%20munitions%20hunting%20down%20the%20Geran-2%2C%20Russia's%20domestically%20produced%20analog%20of%20the%20Iranian%20Shahed-136%20long-range%20attack%20drone.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20made%20of%20foam%20or%20plywood%2C%20the%20Gerbera%20is%20more%20expendable%20than%20the%20Geran-2%2C%20which%20has%20an%20estimated%20price%20of%20between%20%2435%2C000%20and%20%2480%2C000%20each.%20Gerberas%20cost%20about%20%2410%2C000%20each%20to%20make%2C%20Ukrainian%20officials%20estimated%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThough%20Russia%20has%2C%20more%20recently%2C%20been%20seen%20equipping%20Gerberas%20with%20small%20warheads%20or%20using%20them%20as%20scouting%20tools%2C%20the%20propeller-driven%20drones%20are%20typically%20considered%20distractions%20or%20low-priority%20targets.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBeskrestnov%20wrote%20that%20Russia%20has%20traditionally%20saved%20heavily%20on%20costs%20for%20the%20Gerbera%2C%20initially%20launching%20them%20without%20jamming%20protection%20at%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20later%20began%20fitting%20cheaper%2C%20Iranian%20four-element%20antennas%20to%20the%20drones%2C%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERussia%20sometimes%20equips%20its%20attack%20drones%20with%20even%20more%20advanced%2C%2016-element%20antennas%20%E2%80%94%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussia-level-up-shahed-drones-chinese-antenna-bypass-jammers-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esome%20of%20Chinese%20make%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20but%20Beskrestnov%20said%20on%20Wednesday%20that%20these%20were%20still%20being%20reserved%20for%20%26quot%3Bimportant%20products.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Kyiv%20said%20it%20used%20its%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-flamingo-video-missiles-strike-russia-deep-military-industrial-2026-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehomegrown%20Flamingo%20missiles%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20strike%20a%20production%20facility%20for%20anti-jamming%20antennas%2C%20the%20VNIIR-Progress%20complex%20in%20the%20Russian%20city%20of%20Cheboksary%2C%20about%20600%20miles%20from%20the%20Ukrainian%20border.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plant%20has%20regularly%20come%20under%20attack%20f