dedication%20it%20takes%20to%20thrive%20and%20the%20thrill%20of%20accomplishing%20a%20goal.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWhile%20devoting%20so%20much%20of%20my%20life%20to%20running%2C%20I%20learned%20to%20accept%20myself%20with%20kindness%20after%20a%20bad%20race.%20I%20didn't%20let%20a%20single%20race%20define%20all%20my%20effort%20and%20potential.%20I%20learned%20that%20the%20whole%20experience%20matters.%20I%20truly%20loved%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmental-tricks-to-go-running-2016-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebeing%20a%20runner%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rain%20or%20shine%2C%20putting%20one%20foot%20in%20front%20of%20the%20other%20on%20the%20track%20and%20cross-country%20trails%2C%20and%20I%20chose%20to%20do%20it%20just%20for%20me.%20Winning%20was%20nice%2C%20but%20for%20me%2C%20it%20wasn't%20everything.%20I%20loved%20the%20action%20of%20it%2C%20being%20in%20the%20moment%2C%20I%20felt%20happy%20while%20running%2C%20most%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22692%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author's%20son%20plays%20soccer.%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6a0b6e4b94eb4c909fb2da1e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22519%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20said%20that%20she%20has%20noticed%20the%20sidelines%20at%20her%20children's%20games%20and%20practices%20are%20lined%20with%20people%20yelling%20more%20than%20ever%20%E2%80%94%20and%20not%20always%20for%20the%20right%20reasons.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Isobella%20Jade.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ENow%20that%20my%20own%20kids%20are%2011%20and%2013%20it%20seems%20like%20the%20fields%2C%20courts%2C%20and%20arenas%20they%20play%20in%20get%20louder%20as%20the%20years%20go%20by.%20Unfortunately%2C%20they're%20not%20always%20filled%20with%20the%20positive%20energy%20that%20pushed%20me%20when%20I%20was%20their%20age.%20Over%20the%20years%2C%20I've%20heard%20parents%20and%20spectators%20yell%20aggressively%20at%20kids%20while%20they%20are%20playing