0the%20time%2C%26quot%3B%20I%20often%20tell%20my%20kids.%20I%20want%20them%20to%20know%20that%20playing%20for%20the%20love%20of%20the%20game%20means%20caring%20about%20the%20act%20of%20playing%20a%20sport%20for%20the%20pure%20joy%20of%20it%2C%20for%20the%20love%20of%20the%20experience.%20It's%20a%20feeling%20of%20happiness%20while%20showing%20effort%2C%20passion%2C%20and%20dedication%2C%20not%20to%20mention%20the%20willingness%20to%20overcome%20obstacles%20and%20learning%20to%20have%20a%20positive%20attitude.%20I%20need%20my%20kids%20to%20know%20that%20the%20trophies%20and%20awards%20aren't%20everything.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%225f281efc-8add-4dc0-afca-2b0772e3b1af%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI'm%20seeing%20a%20difference%20in%20my%20children%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fplaying-sports-is-secret-to-womens-success-2014-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPlaying%20a%20sport%3C%2Fa%3E%20should%20increase%20your%20joy%2C%20boost%20your%20mood%2C%20and%20teach%20you%20about%20teamwork.%20Once%20that%20happens%2C%20I%20believe%2C%20other%20opportunities%20and%20successes%20will%20follow%20naturally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20culture%20of%20hypercompetitiveness%2C%20I'm%20not%20falling%20for%20the%20pressure%20to%20succeed%2C%20comparisons%2C%20and%20tears.%20When%20I%20watch%20my%20kids%20give%20their%20all%2C%20I%20mostly%20care%20about%20them%20making%20positive%20memories%2C%20and%20I%20hope%20this%20time%20in%20their%20lives%20will%20be%20something%20good%20to%20look%20back%20on%2C%20not%20bring%20flashbacks%20of%20distress%20based%20on%20what%20the%20score%20was%20years%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20when%20my%20daughter%20was%20deciding%20what%20sport%20to%20focus%20on%2C%20I%20told%20her%20to%20imagine%20if%20the%20team%20lost%2C%20if%20the%20team%20wasn't%20as%20strong%2C%20if%20she%20wasn't%20a%20top%20player%2C%20what%20sport%20or%20activity%20would%20she%20choose%20to%20do%20for%20the%20