0income%20of%20Rs%201%20crore%20per%20year.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20not%20being%20able%20to%20go%20abroad%20for%20his%20studies%2C%20he%20has%20now%20been%20able%20to%20send%20both%20his%20sons%20abroad%20for%20their%20education%20(one%20of%20whom%20has%20returned%20to%20help%20him)%2C%20bought%20a%20house%2C%20over%2030%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20along%20with%20the%20latest%20equipment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAll%20this%20happened%20thanks%20to%20carrot%20farming.%20They%20never%20broke%20my%20heart%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPhuman%20Singh%E2%80%99s%20home%20also%20doubles%20up%20as%20a%20carrot%20farming%20school%2C%20where%20he%20helps%20anyone%20interested.%20No%20young%20farmer%20is%20sent%20away%20without%20their%20questions%20being%20answered.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20at%20least%20four%20farmers%20who%20come%20home%20daily%20to%20learn.%20I%20explain%20whatever%20I%20know%20in%20detail.%20I%20even%20visit%20their%20farms%20to%20teach%20them%20practically.%20I%E2%80%99m%20always%20available%20to%20help%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20shares.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20every%20aspiring%20farmer%2C%20he%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CDon%E2%80%99t%20lose%20hope.%20All%20you%20need%20to%20succeed%20is%20determination.%20Nothing%20is%20impossible.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EImages%20Courtesy%20Phuman%20Singh%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757233800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2024-08-30-at-11.52.18-1725875918.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496839%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Over%20the%20past%2030%20years%2C%20Phuman%20Singh%20Kaurra%20from%20Punjab%20has%20been%20turning%20his%20family's%20fortunes%20around%20through%20carrot%20farming.%20He%20also%20has%20a%20seed%20bank%20that%20can%20cultivate%20up%20to%20650%20acres%20of%20land.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Sowmya%20Mani%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496839%2Fpunjab-farmer-phuman-singh-carrot-farming-earns-crores%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%203%20Million%20Trees%20Brought%20Back%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Revived%20Wildlife%20%26amp%3B%20Created%20Jobs%20for%20Thousands%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20is%20something%20different%20in%20the%20air%20now%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Inderjit%20Singh%2C%20a%2079-year-old%20farmer%20from%20Rajinder%20Nagar%20in%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20Fatehgarh%20Sahib%20district.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20feels%20cleaner.%20Birds%20sing%20all%20day%2C%20and%20when%20I%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F446298%2Fjunnar-family-revives-forest-digs-70-trenches-plants-450-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewalk%20through%20the%20trees%20I%20planted%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20it%20feels%20like%20a%20forest%20that%20belongs%20to%20all%20of%20us.%E2%80%9D%20His%20voice%20carries%20the%20pride%20of%20a%20man%20who%20has%20watched%20life%20return%20to%20land%20once%20left%20barren.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20far%20from%20his%20village%2C%20in%20Lang%2C%2032-year-old%20Romanpreet%20Singh%20shares%20a%20similar%20experience.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20never%20imagined%20anything%20could%20grow%20on%20that%20patch%20of%20land%20near%20the%20crematorium.%20It%20was%20dry%20and%20forgotten.%20Now%20it%20is%20buzzing%20with%20butterflies%20and%20birds%2C%20and%20it%20has%20created%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20It%20brought%20our%20village%20together.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496504%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20reflections%20capture%20a%20larger%20transformation%20taking%20root%20across%20rural%20Punjab.%20It%20is%20a%20movement%20of%20ecological%20renewal%20and%20communal%20healing%2C%20driven%20by%20a%20growing%20network%20of%20native%20forests%20that%20are%20reviving%20ecosystems%2C%20replenishing%20groundwater%2C%20and%20restoring%20dignity%20to%20those%20who%20care%20for%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EOne%20man%E2%80%99s%20love%20letter%20to%20Punjab%20%E2%80%93%20The%20vision%20behind%20the%20movement%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20force%20behind%20this%20change%20is%20the%20Roundglass%20Foundation%2C%20led%20by%20its%20founder%2C%20Gurpreet%20Sunny%20Singh%2C%20whose%20lifelong%20bond%20with%20Punjab%20fuels%20his%20vision%20of%20environmental%20and%20social%20renewal.%20He%20speaks%20of%20the%20land%20with%20reverence%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496559%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%20was%20started%20in%20March%202019%20to%20promote%20planting%20trees%20in%20Punjab%20villages%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPunjab%20is%20not%20just%20a%20state%20to%20me%3B%20it%20is%20a%20breathing%20heritage.%20The%20environmental%20challenges%20we%20face%20are%20not%20isolated%3B%20they%20are%20symptoms%20of%20a%20larger%20disconnect%20between%20communities%20and%20nature.%20Our%20work%20is%20about%20restoring%20that%20bond%2C%20nurturing%20both%20land%20and%20life%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20tells%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20him%2C%20it%20is%20not%20just%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F474029%2Fjagdish-kuniyal-tree-planting-uttarakhand%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eplanting%20trees%20but%20about%20cultivating%20a%20future%3C%2Fa%3E%20where%20nature%2C%20culture%2C%20and%20community%20grow%20in%20unison.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGuiding%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20afforestation%20efforts%20is%20Vishal%20Chowla%2C%20project%20lead%20of%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20(TBTP)%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20an%20initiative%20to%20rebuild%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20green%20cover%20by%20reintroducing%20native%20tree%20species%20to%20depleted%20landscapes.%20He%20recalls%20the%20early%20days%20vividly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20I%20first%20visited%20these%20villages%2C%20the%20soil%20was%20exhausted%20and%20the%20air%20heavy%20with%20pollution.%20We%20knew%20planting%20trees%20was%20essential%2C%20but%20the%20real%20challenge%20was%20to%20plant%20hope%2C%20livelihoods%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20ownership%20among%20the%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20seed%20of%20hope%20was%20first%20sown%20in%20March%202019%2C%20when%20the%20foundation%20planted%20saplings%20on%20government%20land%20in%20Badaushi%20Kalan%20village.%20It%20was%20a%20modest%20start%2C%20but%20rooted%20in%20the%20idea%20of%20reviving%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20biodiversity%20with%20native%20species%20like%20desi%20beri%2C%20dhaak%2C%20phulai%2C%20and%20farah.%20These%20hardy%20trees%2C%20once%20central%20to%20the%20state%E2%80%99s%20natural%20identity%2C%20restore%20soil%20and%20water%20systems%2C%20support%20wildlife%20habitats%2C%20and%20withstand%20climate%20extremes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Roundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20that%20the%20initiative%20continues%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200243.346_11zon-1756996410-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496565%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ERoundglass%20Foundation%20encourages%20and%20educates%20the%20youth%20to%20plant%20native%20trees%20in%20their%20villages%2C%20so%20that%20the%20initiative%20continues%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20that%20single%20pilot%2C%20the%20project%20has%20spread%20like%20the%20roots%20of%20a%20forest%2C%20reaching%20over%201%2C600%20villages%20with%20more%20than%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20planted.%20The%20model%20is%20as%20much%20social%20as%20it%20is%20environmental.%20TBTP%20stresses%20not%20only%20planting%20but%20also%20long-term%20care.%20Saplings%20are%20nurtured%20for%20up%20to%2030%20months%2C%20creating%20steady%20employment%20for%20local%20residents%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20women%20and%20youth%2C%20who%20make%20up%2070%25%20of%20the%20caregiving%20workforce.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhat%20happens%20after%20planting%3F%20The%20work%20that%20matters%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20is%20only%20the%20start.%20The%20real%20effort%20is%20in%20the%20care%20%E2%80%94%20watering%2C%20pruning%2C%20and%20protecting%20%E2%80%94%20until%20the%20trees%20can%20stand%20on%20their%20own%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20Gurpreet%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CEmpowering%20youth%20through%20this%20work%20is%20important.%20It%20is%20about%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F467221%2Freeva-sood-chemical-free-farming-empower-rural-women-agriva-naturally%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Einstilling%20purpose%2C%20building%20self-reliance%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20reshaping%20how%20communities%20view%20their%20future.%20When%20young%20people%20become%20guardians%20of%20these%20forests%2C%20they%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20protect%20the%20environment%2C%20they%20lead%20their%20communities%20towards%20change.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Inderjit%20and%20many%20others%2C%20this%20change%20has%20become%20deeply%20personal.%20A%20seasoned%20cultivator%2C%20he%20had%20long%20watched%20his%20soil%20decline.%20He%20offered%20a%20kanal%20of%20his%20private%20land%20to%20the%20project%20with%20cautious%20optimism.%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20sceptical%20at%20first%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20admits.%20%E2%80%9CI%20had%20tried%20planting%20before%2C%20but%20the%20trees%20didn%E2%80%99t%20survive.%20When%20Roundglass%20came%2C%20they%20stayed%2C%20cared%20for%20the%20saplings%2C%20and%20involved%20us%20in%20the%20process.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20his%20land%20hosts%20a%20flourishing%20mini%20forest%20of%20nearly%20three%20kanals%20with%20over%20700%20trees%20from%20more%20than%20100%20varieties%2C%20including%20peepal%2C%20neem%2C%20and%20jhand.%20The%20impact%20has%20been%20striking.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20a%20diverse%20forest%2C%20resilient%20and%20alive.%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F410969%2Fretirement-teacher-turns-barren-hill-thriving-forest-madhya-pradesh%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBirds%20have%20returned%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20my%20crops%20have%20improved%20because%20they%20eat%20the%20pests%20naturally.%20I%E2%80%99ve%20reduced%20chemical%20sprays%2C%20and%20the%20soil%20feels%20richer.%20It%20is%20a%20gift%20to%20the%20next%20generation%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says%2C%20his%20voice%20heavy%20with%20emotion.%20%E2%80%9CPeople%20once%20questioned%20why%20I%20was%20so%20involved%20in%20The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project.%20Now%2C%20they%20come%20and%20sit%20in%20the%20forest.%20It%20is%20peaceful%20and%20has%20united%20the%20whole%20village.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EBirdsong%20and%20biodiversity%20%E2%80%93%20When%20nature%20returns%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20tells%20a%20similar%20story%20of%20renewal.%20%E2%80%9CThe%20dry%20patch%20near%20the%20crematorium%20was%20lifeless%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20TBTP%20came%20to%20our%20village%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20trees.%20It%20brought%20work%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20for%20women%20and%20youth%20%E2%80%94%20who%20watered%2C%20tended%2C%20and%20protected%20the%20saplings.%20It%20gave%20us%20purpose%20and%20pride.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20foundation%20has%20planted%20around%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20so%20far%20in%20the%20villages%20%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T200645.054_11zon-1756996644-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496570%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20foundation%20has%20planted%20around%20three%20million%20native%20trees%20so%20far%20in%20the%20villages%20%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%20time%2C%20what%20was%20barren%20became%20green%20and%20alive.%20%E2%80%9CNow%20we%20see%20prinias%2C%20kingfishers%2C%20coucals%2C%20purple%20sunbirds%2C%20and%20sparrows%20all%20the%20time.%20The%20ecosystem%20is%20healing%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20mini%20forests%20are%20not%20isolated%20patches%20but%20part%20of%20a%20wider%20ecological%20strategy.%20Beyond%20shade%20and%20beauty%2C%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F477262%2Fvikrant-tongad-founder-safe-transforms-dumpsite-in-greater-noida-plants-trees%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Enative%20trees%20conserve%20water%2C%20regenerate%20soil%20health%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20support%20biodiversity.%20Vishal%20explains%2C%20%E2%80%9CTrees%20improve%20soil%20moisture%2C%20reduce%20evaporation%2C%20and%20create%20micro-channels%20that%20hold%20rainwater.%20An%20acre%20of%20forest%20can%20save%20over%2012%20million%20litres%20of%20water%20annually%20compared%20to%20conventional%20paddy%20fields.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGurpreet%20reinforces%20the%20connection%3A%20%E2%80%9CWater%20and%20trees%20are%20intertwined.%20By%20protecting%20one%2C%20we%20safeguard%20the%20other.%20Punjab%E2%80%99s%20future%20depends%20on%20this%20balance.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWho%20owns%20a%20mini%20forest%3F%20The%20power%20of%20local%20pride%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20balance%20is%20being%20rebuilt%20not%20through%20imposition%20but%20collaboration.%20Much%20of%20the%20land%20is%20government-owned%2C%20but%20when%20individuals%20like%20Inderjit%20offer%20private%20land%2C%20it%20fosters%20co-ownership%20and%20responsibility.%20%E2%80%9CVillages%20take%20ownership%2C%20and%20that%20is%20why%20survival%20rates%20of%20trees%20are%20so%20high%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20many%20places%2C%20schools%20are%20involved%2C%20turning%20forests%20into%20living%20classrooms%20where%20children%20learn%20about%20ecology%20and%20conservation.%20%E2%80%9CChildren%20see%20the%20trees%20grow%20and%20learn%20to%20respect%20nature%2C%E2%80%9D%20Inderjit%20smiles.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20plants%20seeds%20of%20awareness%20that%20will%20last%20generations.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20planting%20a%20few%20saplings%20in%20one%20village%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20has%20grown%20into%20a%20statewide%20movement%20spanning%2017%20districts.%20Each%20of%20the%20three%20million%20trees%20has%20been%20carefully%20tracked%2C%20with%20survival%20rates%20monitored%20through%20rigorous%20documentation%20and%20local%20engagement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%20500px)%20100vw%2C%20500px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-500x375.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-500x375.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-300x225.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-768x576.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-1200x900.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-800x600.jpg%20800w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-600x450.jpg%20600w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-400x300.jpg%20400w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-200x150.jpg%20200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907-150x113.jpg%20150w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FWhatsApp-Image-2025-08-14-at-13.10.25_87c06412-2_11zon-1756996907.jpg%201280w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496574%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22375%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20native%20trees%20help%20to%20use%20water%20wisely%20and%20improve%20the%20health%20of%20the%20soil%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20don%E2%80%99t%20just%20plant%20and%20walk%20away%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20map%20each%20site%20using%20KML%20Polygons%20%E2%80%94%20satellite-based%20tools%20that%20log%20the%20exact%20coordinates%20of%20every%20mini%20forest.%20This%20lets%20us%20maintain%20a%20digital%20record%2C%20verify%20locations%2C%20and%20track%20growth.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EHow%20forests%20are%20feeding%20families%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20project%E2%80%99s%20social%20impact%20matches%20its%20ecological%20gains.%20Beyond%20trees%2C%20it%20has%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F418054%2Fneeti-goel-restaurateur-mumbai-khaanachiye-lb-trust-sundarbans-tiger-widows%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebecome%20a%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20thousands%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20rural%20Punjab.%20Around%20120%20people%20work%20at%20its%20nurseries%2C%20and%20the%20initiative%20collaborates%20with%20the%20Mahatma%20Gandhi%20National%20Rural%20Employment%20Guarantee%20Act%20(MGNREGA)%20to%20scale%20up%20plantations.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20end%20of%202024%2C%20TBTP%20had%20generated%20more%20than%2015%2C000%20jobs%20through%20MGNREGA%2C%20most%20filled%20by%20women%20and%20young%20people.%20These%20roles%20extend%20beyond%20wages%2C%20involving%20environmental%20custodianship%20from%20land%20preparation%20to%20sapling%20care.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMGNREGA%20has%20been%20instrumental%20in%20bringing%20in%20local%20workers%20who%20not%20only%20earn%20but%20also%20develop%20a%20sense%20of%20responsibility%20towards%20the%20land.%20When%20someone%20helps%20raise%20a%20forest%20from%20scratch%2C%20it%20becomes%20personal%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%20Vishal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20has%20watched%20young%20people%20grow%20into%20community%20leaders%20through%20this%20work.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20educate%20their%20neighbours%2C%20advocate%20for%20conservation%2C%20and%20carry%20the%20torch%20forward%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20sun%20sets%20over%20Rajinder%20Nagar%2C%20Inderjit%20walks%20slowly%20through%20his%20forest.%20%E2%80%9CThis%20is%20the%20Punjab%20I%20remember%20as%20a%20child%20%E2%80%94%20lush%2C%20vibrant%2C%20alive.%20It%20is%20coming%20back%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%20In%20Lang%2C%20Romanpreet%20watches%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F493007%2Fbutterfly-friendly-plants-for-indian-homes-marigold-hibiscus-tulsi%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ebutterflies%20flit%20through%20the%20branches%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T201626.909_11zon-1756997217-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496582%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%20helps%20to%20plant%20trees%20and%20is%20a%20consistent%20source%20of%20livelihood%20for%20many%20villagers%2C%20especially%20women%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUltimately%2C%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20not%20only%20about%20greening%20land%20but%20about%20rekindling%20identity%2C%20reviving%20community%2C%20and%20reimagining%20a%20future%20in%20harmony%20with%20nature.%20Gurpreet%20puts%20it%20aptly%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CPlanting%20a%20tree%20is%20an%20act%20of%20faith%20in%20the%20future.%20It%20is%20a%20promise%20that%20we%20care%2C%20that%20we%20will%20nurture%2C%20and%20that%20we%20believe%20in%20the%20resilience%20of%20this%20land%20and%20its%20people.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20pictures%20courtesy%20Roundglass%20Foundation%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757215800000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FBlue-and-Yellow-Modern-Business-Workshop-Facebook-Ad-2025-09-04T195457.273_11zon-1756995925.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496504%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Roundglass%20Foundation%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98The%20Billion%20Tree%20Project%E2%80%99%20has%20planted%20over%203%20million%20native%20trees%20across%20Punjab%2C%20restoring%20biodiversity%2C%20improving%20soil%20and%20water%20health%2C%20and%20creating%20thousands%20of%20jobs%20for%20women%20and%20youth.%20Learn%20how%20this%20movement%20is%20improving%20lives.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Raajwrita%20Dutta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496504%2Froundglass-foundation-the-billion-tree-project-planting-native-trees-in-villages-livelihoods%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Farmer%20Turns%20Cashew%20Crop%20Ruined%20By%20Rains%20into%20Sprouts%2C%20Pickles%20%26amp%3B%20More%3B%20Earns%20Rs%2025%20Lakh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20interviews%20and%20reporting%20for%20this%20story%20were%20conducted%20in%20September%202024.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20large%20produce%20of%20wet%2C%20harvested%20cashews%20was%20in%20front%20of%20Brijith%20Krishnan.%20The%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20his%20hometown%20in%20Kerala%20had%20ruined%20the%20crop%20again.%20He%20knew%20this%20crop%20wouldn%E2%80%99t%20fetch%20him%20any%20income.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAround%20the%20same%20time%20in%202020%2C%20the%20mechanical%20engineering%20diploma%20holder%20also%20faced%20another%20challenging%20turn%20of%20events%20when%20he%20unexpectedly%20lost%20his%20job%20as%20a%20supervisor%20in%20an%20IT%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A496857%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20addition%20to%20this%2C%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20%E2%80%93%20a%20traditional%20source%20of%20income%20for%20his%20family%20%E2%80%93%20was%20also%20on%20the%20decline.%20This%20double%20blow%20left%20him%20without%20a%20stable%20income%20source.%20He%20strived%20to%20permanently%20settle%20in%20his%20hometown%20and%20explore%20new%20avenues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20keen%20eye%20for%20innovation%20and%20a%20determination%20to%20make%20a%20meaningful%20impact%2C%20he%20observed%20the%20growing%20trend%20towards%20plant-based%20diets%2C%20particularly%20in%20the%20vegan%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeveraging%20his%20mechanical%20engineering%20background%20and%20driven%20by%20a%20desire%20to%20create%20value%20in%20cashew%20farming%2C%20he%20delved%20into%20the%20unchartered%20territory%20of%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F17187%2Fyoung-innovator-created-one-kind-cashew-nut-grading-machine%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashew%20nuts%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20he%20officially%20launched%20his%20venture%2C%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%2C%20which%20makes%20dishes%20from%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala%2C%20Bengaluru%2C%20Mumbai.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20such%20as%20cashew%20sprouts%2C%20soup%20premix%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20more.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364789%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20such%20as%20cashew%20sprouts%2C%20soup%20premix%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EReality%20of%20the%20largest%20cashew%20producers%20of%20Kerala%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Cashew%20Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20published%20by%20the%20ICAR-%20Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%E2%80%99%2C%20the%20coastal%20state%20of%20Kerala%20accounts%20for%2015%20percent%20of%20cashew%20production%20in%20India.%20Of%20this%2C%20Kannur%20district%20accounts%20for%20nearly%2063%20percent%20of%20the%20total%20cashew%20cultivation%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECashew%20production%20is%20relatively%20high%20in%20Kannur%20because%20the%20region%20experiences%20a%20prolonged%20dry%20spell%20during%20the%20reproductive%20phase%20of%20the%20crop.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBrijith%2C%20who%20hails%20from%20the%20same%20district%20and%20grows%20cashew%20on%2013%20acres%20of%20land%2C%20shares%20that%20cashew%20productivity%20has%20been%20affected%20amid%20unseasonal%20rain%20and%20extreme%20weather%20conditions%20in%20the%20last%20few%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20experience%20unseasonal%20rains%20in%20March-May.%20This%20affects%20the%20pollination%20process%20and%20the%20harvesting%20period.%20We%20are%20small%20farmers%2C%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20good%20storage%20facilities.%20As%20a%20result%2C%20we%20have%20to%20keep%20our%20harvest%20out%20in%20the%20open.%20Most%20of%20this%20produce%20gets%20wet%20in%20this%20period%20then.%20No%20cashew%20factory%20is%20ready%20to%20purchase%20this%20damaged%20product%20as%20its%20quality%20becomes%20poor%2C%20colour%20gets%20faded%2C%20and%20also%20has%20a%20poor%20taste%2C%E2%80%9D%20shares%20the%2047-year-old.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-2-1725551452-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364788%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20makes%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20supplies%20to%20major%20food%20supply%20companies%20and%20hotels%20in%20Kerala.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20conventional%20practice%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F181811%2Fias-hero-odisha-district-cashew-empowerment-farmers-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecashew%20farming%20%3C%2Fa%3Einvolves%20harvesting%20the%20nuts%20for%20consumption%20as%20dry%20fruits%20or%20in%20a%20roasted%20form%2C%20there%20was%20a%20limited%20scope%20for%20value%20addition.%20%E2%80%9CYou%20can%20dry%20and%20store%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F354850%2Fhomemaker-entrepreneur-organic-coconut-greenaura-oil-pickles-business-kerala-sumila-jayaraj%2F%23google_vignette%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecoconut%20produce%20%3C%2Fa%3Eand%20can%20make%20mango%20pulp%20but%20there%20is%20hardly%20any%20alternative%20to%20utilise%20cashews%20in%20other%20forms%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecognising%20this%20as%20a%20crucial%20gap%20in%20the%20market%2C%20Brijith%20embarked%20on%20a%20journey%20of%20experimentation.%20He%20reached%20out%20to%20institutions%20like%20Central%20Food%20Technological%20Research%20Institute%20(CFTRI)%20Mysuru%2C%20and%20Kerala%20Agriculture%20University%20to%20explore%20the%20nutritional%20benefits%20and%20viability%20of%20sprouting%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20receiving%20an%20encouraging%20response%20from%20the%20institutes%2C%20his%20focus%20shifted%20towards%20refining%20the%20sprouting%20technology%20for%20cashews.%20Recognising%20the%20perishable%20nature%20of%20cashews%20and%20the%20challenges%20in%20maintaining%20a%20cold%20supply%20chain%2C%20he%20drew%20inspiration%20from%20Japan%E2%80%99s%20retorting%20technology%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20which%20involves%20heat-treating%20food%20in%20airtight%20containers%20to%20extend%20shelf%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBy%20adapting%20this%20innovative%20approach%2C%20he%20devised%20a%20method%20to%20process%20and%20store%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20room%20temperature%2C%20enhancing%20their%20shelf%20life%20and%20market%20reach.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%20into%20research%20and%20development%2C%20Brijith%20started%20his%20own%20startup%20in%202021.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFrom%20raw%20sprouts%2C%20pickles%20to%20manchurian%2C%20soup%20premix%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20initial%20challenges%20that%20Brijith%20tackled%20was%20the%20limited%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews.%20%E2%80%9CDue%20to%20their%20seasonal%20nature%2C%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20matured%20cashews%20was%20only%2090%20days.%20Therefore%2C%20year%20round%20availability%20was%20a%20big%20concern.%20Through%20persistent%20research%2C%20trials%2C%20and%20development%20efforts%2C%20I%20successfully%20extended%20the%20germination%20potential%20to%20180-200%20days%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20an%20initial%20investment%20of%20Rs%201%20lakh%2C%20Brijith%20secured%20a%20grant%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20from%20the%20central%20government%20under%20the%20Rashtriya%20Krishi%20Vikas%20Yojana%20(RKVY)%20scheme%20that%20aims%20at%20promoting%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship.%20This%20helped%20him%20kickstart%20the%20work.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Brijith%20foccussed%20on%20improving%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20in%20order%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1725551361-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-364786%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EBrijith%20focussed%20on%20improving%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20to%20commercialise%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20products.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%2C%20he%20offers%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20value-added%20products%20%E2%80%93%20cashew%20sprouts%20Manchurian%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20butter%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Emalai%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20schezwan%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20Malabar%20%3Cem%3Emasala%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20%3Cem%3Etheyal%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20soup%20premix%2C%20cashew%20sprouts%20brine%2C%20pickles%2C%20and%20fresh%20cashew%20sprouts.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20meticulous%20focus%20on%20quality%20and%20value%2C%20Brijith%20priced%20his%20sprouted%20cashews%20at%20Rs%201%2C000%20per%20kg.%20Through%20strategic%20partnerships%20with%20celebrity%20chefs%2C%20star%20hotels%2C%20and%20catering%20groups%2C%20Brijith%20positioned%20his%20premium%20cashew%20sprout%20products%20in%20a%20niche%20market%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20his%20regular%20customers%20Thomas%2C%20who%20works%20as%20a%20corporate%20chef%20at%20Paragon%20group%20of%20restaurants%2C%20shares%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20experienced%20these%20cashew%20sprouts%20can%20be%20included%20in%20a%20healthy%20diet%20and%20lots%20of%20various%20dishes%20can%20be%20prepared%20with%20adaptability.%20It%20is%20not%20easily%20available%20in%20stores%20so%20people%20have%20some%20curiosity%20about%20it.%20These%20dishes%20are%20repeatedly%20demanded%20from%20our%20happy%20customers%20at%20the%20restaurant.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20unique%20positioning%20in%20the%20market%20enabled%20Brijith%20to%20secure%20a%20steady%20clientele%20and%20achieve%20a%20turnover%20of%20Rs%2025%20lakh%20in%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20his%20endeavours%20were%20not%20only%20driven%20by%20a%20passion%20for%20innovation%20but%20also%20by%20a%20commitment%20to%20empower%20local%20farmers.%20By%20purchasing%20wet%20cashews%20from%20at%20least%2011%20local%20farmers%2C%20Brijith%20managed%20to%20provide%20a%20sustainable%20solution%20by%20transforming%20them%20into%20high-quality%20sprouted%20cashews.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CBy%20reimagining%20traditional%20practices%20and%20leveraging%20modern%20technology%2C%20I%20not%20only%20wanted%20to%20revitalise%20the%20cashew%20farming%20industry%20but%20also%20exemplify%20the%20potential%20for%20agri-business%20entrepreneurship%20to%20drive%20economic%20growth%20in%20rural%20communities.%20I%20am%20glad%20that%20we%20don%E2%80%99t%20have%20to%20worry%20about%20wet%20produce%20anymore%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAll%20photos%3A%20Brijith%20Krishnan%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ESources%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%5Cn%3Ch5%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcashew.icar.gov.in%2Faicrpc%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F03%2FStatus-of-Cashew-Research-.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Status%20of%20Cashew%20Research%20and%20Development%20in%20India%3A%20A%20State%20Perspective%20%3C%2Fa%3Epublished%20by%20Dr%20M%20Gangadhara%20Nayak%2C%20Director%2C%20ICAR-Directorate%20of%20Cashew%20Research%2C%20Karnataka%20in%20November%202018.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fh5%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757147400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fcashew-1-1725551491.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496857%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kerala-based%20farmer%20Brijith%20Krishnan%20started%20Eatery%20Malbarikas%20which%20makes%20dishes%20using%20sprouted%20cashew%20nuts.%20Interestingly%2C%20he%20enhanced%20the%20germination%20potential%20of%20cashews%20and%20helps%20fellow%20cashew%20farmers%20as%20well.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22Shivani%20Gupta%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F496857%2Fkerala-farmer-wet-cashews-value-added-products%2F%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22A%20Rs%205000%20Budget%20Guide%20to%20Exploring%20Karnala%E2%80%99s%20Forests%2C%20Fort%20%26amp%3B%20Birdlife%2C%20Just%20an%20Hour%20From%20Mumbai%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EVisualise%20a%20place%20where%20forest%20trails%20wind%20beneath%20thick%20green%20canopies%2C%20where%20rare%20birds%20call%20from%20treetops%2C%20and%20where%20an%20ancient%20fort%20watches%20over%20the%20valley%20from%20above.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJust%2064%20km%20from%20Mumbai%20lies%20Karnala%2C%20a%20tranquil%20haven%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F394231%2Fbest-birdwatching-destinations-india-winter-migration-rajasthan-gujarat-kerala%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eknown%20for%20its%20bird%20sanctuary%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20historic%20Karnala%20Fort.%20With%20fresh%20air%2C%20natural%20beauty%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20adventure%2C%20Karnala%20makes%20the%20perfect%20destination%20for%20a%20relaxed%20family%20getaway.%20Best%20of%20all%2C%20it%20can%20be%20experienced%20on%20a%20modest%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20five-day%20trip%20for%20a%20family%20of%20three%20can%20be%20comfortably%20enjoyed%20on%20a%20budget%20of%20Rs%204%2C000%20to%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%20including%20transport%2C%20food%2C%20accommodation%2C%20entry%20tickets%2C%20and%20local%20travel.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Ca%20data-tracker%3D%5C%22%7B%26quot%3Barticle_name%26quot%3B%3A%26quot%3BArticle%20Page%20Ad%20Banner%26quot%3B%2C%26quot%3Bposition%26quot%3B%3A1%2C%26quot%3Barticle_id%26quot%3B%3A494788%7D%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcampaign.thebetterindia.com%2Ftbi-showcase%2F%5C%22%20data-carousel%3D%5C%22adbanner%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Article%20Ad%20Banner%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F08%2Fad-banner-1756106894.jpg%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fa%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EDay%201%3A%20Mumbai%20to%20Panvel%20%E2%80%93%20Gateway%20to%20nature%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EStart%20your%20trip%20by%20boarding%20a%20suburban%20local%20train%20from%20Mumbai%20to%20Panvel.%20Trains%20run%20frequently%20and%20cost%20just%20Rs%2015%20to%20Rs%2025%20per%20person.%20The%20journey%20takes%20around%20an%20hour%2C%20depending%20on%20your%