as%3C%2Fem%3E.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20response%2C%20she%20says%2C%20has%20been%20steadily%20growing.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20didn%E2%80%99t%20take%20off%20immediately%2C%20but%20now%20I%20get%20new%20queries%20almost%20every%20day.%E2%80%9D%20Each%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Etakes%20two%20to%20three%20days%20to%20make%2C%20depending%20on%20the%20number%20of%20flowers%20and%20the%20design.%20She%20uses%20acrylic%20yarn%20and%20adds%20beads%20to%20bind%20the%20flowers%20together.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20Zainab%2C%20the%20appeal%20lies%20in%20the%20emotional%20value.%20%E2%80%9CNothing%20goes%20to%20waste.%20The%20flowers%20don%E2%80%99t%20wilt.%20It%E2%80%99s%20handmade%20with%20love%20and%20care%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20something%20couples%20can%20keep%20forever.%20I%20feel%20weddings%20are%20moving%20towards%20more%20sustainable%2C%20mindful%20choices%2C%20and%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Efit%20right%20into%20that.%20The%20best%20part%20is%20how%20sentimental%20they%20are%20and%20full%20of%20soul.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EWhy%20crochet%2C%20why%20now%3F%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Esays%20a%20lot%20about%20how%20Indian%20weddings%20are%20evolving.%20Once%20notorious%20for%20their%20extravagance%20and%20waste%2C%20younger%20couples%20are%20increasingly%20seeking%20ways%20to%20make%20their%20celebrations%20more%20personal%20and%20sustainable.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%E2%80%99m%20always%20on%20the%20lookout%20for%20fresh%20trends%20and%20styles%2C%20so%20when%20I%20came%20across%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20I%20found%20them%20incredibly%20cute%20%E2%80%94%20something%20that%20could%20create%20a%20buzz%20at%20my%20wedding%2C%E2%80%9D%20says%2026-year-old%20Shilpa%2C%20who%20tied%20the%20knot%20in%202024.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20ordered%20white%20%3Cem%3Emogra%3C%2Fem%3E-like%20flowers%20with%20an%20additional%20layer%20of%20crochet%20roses%2C%20and%20the%20whole%20piece%20cost%20me%20around%20Rs%204%2C300.%20The%20varmala%20is%20now%20framed%20in%20my%20living%20room%2C%20and%20it%E2%80%99s%20the%20best%20thing%20to%20see%20when%20I%20wake%20up%20every%20day%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22auto%2C%20(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20varmalas%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T015428.174-1756931451-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-496056%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EFor%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eoffers%20a%20way%20out.%20Image%20courtesy%3A%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fzains_story%2F%3Fhl%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EZain%E2%80%99s%20Story%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFresh%20flowers%2C%20while%20undeniably%20beautiful%2C%20come%20with%20hidden%20costs%2C%20including%20environmental%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20emotional.%20Hours%20of%20refrigeration%2C%20long-distance%20transport%2C%20and%20thousands%20of%20rupees%20spent%20on%20garlands%20that%20last%20barely%20an%20evening.%20For%20couples%20mindful%20of%20their%20carbon%20footprint%20or%20eager%20for%20keepsakes%2C%20crochet%20offers%20a%20way%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20also%20a%20revivalist%20charm%20to%20it.%20Crochet%2C%20once%20dismissed%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cgrandmother%E2%80%99s%20hobby%E2%80%9D%2C%20is%20now%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20slow%20fashion%20and%20handmade%20crafts.%20It%20carries%20a%20nostalgia%2C%20a%20tactile%20softness%2C%20and%20a%20sense%20of%20intimacy%20that%20mass-produced%20items%20lack.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20then%20there%20is%20the%20Instagram%20effect.%20A%20pastel%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eagainst%20a%20cream%20%3Cem%3Esherwani%20%3C%2Fem%3Eor%20a%20red%20%3Cem%3Elehenga%20%3C%2Fem%3Emakes%20for%20striking%20visuals%2C%20fuelling%20curiosity%20and%20desire%20among%20wedding%20planners%20and%20couples%20alike.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EA%20craft%2C%20a%20community%2C%20a%20change%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBehind%20the%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20not%20just%20designers%2C%20but%20entire%20communities%20of%20women%20artisans.%20At%20Enchanted%20Threads%2C%20Ananya%20ensures%2030%20percent%20of%20the%20proceeds%20go%20directly%20to%20her%20team%20of%20underprivileged%20women%20in%20Uttarakhand.%20For%20Manya%2C%20it%20has%20been%20about%20collaboration%20with%20fellow%20crochet%20artists%2C%20slowly%20expanding%20from%20a%20solo%20effort%20to%20a%20small%20creative%20team.%20For%20Zainab%2C%20it%E2%80%99s%20about%20pouring%20herself%20into%20every%20detail%2C%20bead%20by%20bead.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEach%20%3Cem%3Evarmala%20%3C%2Fem%3Eca