tainable%20wedding%20practices%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eare%20no%20longer%20just%20a%20niche%20experiment.%20They%20are%20becoming%20part%20of%20the%20mainstream%20wedding%20vocabulary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eis%20not%20happening%20in%20isolation%3B%20it%20mirrors%20a%20larger%20shift%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F451310%2Fsustainable-wedding-love-story-avinash-tewari-namita-manohar-low-waste-wedding-recycled-decor%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Econscious%20weddings%20across%20India.%3C%2Fa%3E%20Couples%20are%20increasingly%20swapping%20paper-heavy%20invitations%20for%20seed-paper%20cards%20that%20sprout%20into%20plants%2C%20replacing%20plastic-heavy%20d%C3%A9cor%20with%20biodegradable%20alternatives%2C%20and%20even%20turning%20to%20upcycled%20fabrics%20for%20their%20wedding%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESeen%20against%20this%20backdrop%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Ebecome%20more%20than%20just%20a%20pretty%20keepsake%2C%20they%20are%20part%20of%20a%20powerful%20movement%20that%20redefines%20how%20we%20celebrate%20love%2C%20proving%20that%20tradition%20and%20sustainability%20can%20go%20hand%20in%20hand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECouples%20can%20frame%20them%2C%20pass%20them%20down%2C%20or%20simply%20keep%20them%20folded%20away%2C%20soft%20with%20yarn%20and%20memory.%20In%20a%20wedding%20culture%20obsessed%20with%20grandeur%2C%20crochet%20%3Cem%3Evarmalas%20%3C%2Fem%3Eremind%20us%20of%20something%20simpler%20yet%20profound.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELove%2C%20after%20all%2C%20is%20meant%20to%20last.%20Why%20shouldn%E2%80%99t%20the%20garlands%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1757129400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2025%2F09%2FTBI-FEATURED-IMAGE-2025-09-04T014422.986-1756930470.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F%3Fp%3D496018%